quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  2,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  2,1,alif laam mem
  2,2,"yeh Allah ki kitaab hai, is mein koi shak nahi hadaayat hai unn parhaiz gaar logon ke liye"
  2,3,"jo ghaib par imaan laatay hain, namaz qaim karte hain, jo rizaq hum ne unn ko diya hai, uss mein se kharch karte hain"
  2,4,jo kitaab tum par nazil ki gayi hai ( yani quran ) aur jo kitaaben tum se pehlay nazil ki gayi theen un sab par imaan laatay hain aur akhirat par yaqeen rakhtay hain
  2,5,aisay log apne Rab ki taraf se raah raast par hain aur wohi Falah panay walay hain
  2,6,"jin logon ne ( inn baton ko tasleem karne se ) inkaar kar diya, unn ke liye yaksaa hai, khuwa tum inhen khabardaar karo ya nah karo, behar haal woh maan-ne walay nahi hain"
  2,7,Allah ne un ke dilon aur un ke kaanon par mohar laga di hai aur un ki aankhon par parda par gaya hai woh sakht saza ke mustahiq hain
  2,8,"baaz log aisay bhi hain jo kehte hain ke hum Allah par aur akhirat ke din par imaan laaye hain, halaank Dur haqeeqat woh momin nahi hain"
  2,9,"woh Allah aur imaan laane walon ke sath dhoka baazi kar rahay hain, magar darasal woh khud apne aap hi ko dhokay mein daal rahay hain aur inhen is ka shaoor nahi hai"
  2,10,"un ke dilon mein aik bemari hai jisay Allah ne aur ziyada barha diya, aur jo jhoot woh boltay hain, is ki Padaash mein un ke liye dard naak saza hai"
  2,11,jab kabhi un se kaha gaya ke zameen par fasaad barpaa nah karo to unhon ne yahi kaha ke hum to islaah karne walay hain
  2,12,khabardaar! haqeeqat mein yahi log mufsid hain magar inhen shaoor nahi hai
  2,13,"aur jab un se kaha gaya jis terhan dosray log imaan laaye hain isi terhan tum bhi imaan lao to unhon ne yahi jawab diya"" kya hum bewaqfoon ki terhan imaan layein ?"" khabardaar! haqeeqat mein to yeh khud bewaqoof hain, magar yeh jantay nahi hain"
  2,14,"jab yeh ahal imaan se mlitay hain, to kehte hain ke hum imaan laaye hain aur jab alehadgi mein apne shaitano se mlitay hain, to kehte hain ke asal mein to hum tumahray sath hain aur un logon se mehez mazaq kar rahay hain"
  2,15,"Allah un se mazaq kar raha hai, woh un ki rassi daraaz kiye jata hai, aur yeh apni sar kashi mein andhon ki terhan bhataktay chalay jatay hain"
  2,16,"yeh woh log hain jinhon ne hadaayat ke badlay gumraahi khareed li hai, magar yeh soda un ke liye naffa bakhash nahi hai aur yeh hargiz sahih rastay par nahi hain"
  2,17,inn ki misaal aisi hai jaisay aikshakhs ne aag roshan ki aur jab uss ne saaray mahol ko roshan kar diya to Allah ne inn ka noor Basarat salb kar liya aur inhen is haal mein chore diya ke tarikeon mein inhen kuch nazar nahi aata
  2,18,"yeh behray hain, gungay hain, andhay hain, yeh ab nah paltainge"
  2,19,"ya phir un ki misaal yun samjhoo ke aasman se zor ki barish ho rahi hai aur is ke sath andheri ghata aur karrak chamak bhi hai, yeh bijli ke krhake sun kar apni jaanun ke khauf se kaanon mein ungelianthons letay hain aur Allah innmunkareen haq ko har taraf se ghairay mein liye hue hai"
  2,20,"chamak se un ki haalat yeh ho rahi hai ke goya anqareeb bijli inn ki Basarat uchak le jaye gi jab zara kuch roshni inhen mehsoos hoti hai to iss mein kuch daur chal letay hain aur jab un par andhera chhaa jata hai to khar y ho jatay hain Allah chahta to un ki samaat aur Basarat bilkul hi salb kar laita, yaqeenan woh har cheez par Qadir hai"
  2,21,"logo! bandagi ikhtiyar karo apne uss Rab ki jo tumhara aur tum se pehlay jo log ho guzray hain unn sab ka khaaliq hai, tumahray bachney ki tawaqqa isi soorat hosakti hai"
  2,22,"wohi to hai jiss ne tumahray liye zameen ka farsh bichhaya, aasman ki chhat banai, oopar se pani barsaya aur is ke zariye se har terhan ki pedawar nikaal kar tumahray liye rizaq baham pohanchaya pas jab tum yeh jantay ho to dosaron ko Allah ka maday muqabil nah therao"
  2,23,"aur agar tumhe iss amar mein shak hai ke yeh kittab jo hum ne apne bande par utari hai, yeh hamari hai ya nahi, tu is ke manind aik hi sourat bana lao, apne saaray humnawaoan ko bulaa lau, aik Allah ko chore kar baqi jis jis ki chaho, madad le lau, agar tum sachey ho"
  2,24,"to yeh kaam kar ke dikhao, lekin agar tum ne aisa nah kya aur yaqeenan kabhi nahi kar saktay, to daro is aag se jis ka eendhan banain ge ensaan aur pathar, jo muhayya ki gayi hai munkareen haq ke liye"
  2,25,"aur aepeghambar, jo log is kitaab par imaan le ayen aur ( is ke mutabiq ) apne amal durust kar lain, inhen khush khaberi day do ke unn ke liye aisay baagh hain, jin ke neechay nehrein behti hon gi un baghoon ke phal soorat mein duniya ke phalon se mlitay jaltay hunge jab koi phal inhen khanay ko diya jaye ga, to woh kahin ge ke aisay hi phal is se pehlay duniya mein hum ko diye jatay thay un ke liye wahan pakeeza biwiyan hongi, aur woh wahan hamesha rahen ge"
  2,26,"haan, Allah is se hargiz nahi sharmaata ke machar ya is se bhi haqeer tar kisi cheez kitamselain day jo log haq baat ko qubool karne walay hain, woh unhi tamseloonko dekh kar jaan letay hain ke yeh haq hai jo un ke Rab hi ki taraf se aaya hai, aur jo maan-ne walay nahi hain, woh inhen sun kar kehnay lagtay hain ke aisi tamseloonse Allah ko kya sarokaar? is terhan Allah aik hi baat se bahuton ko gumraahi mein mubtala kar deta hai aur bahuton ko raah raast dikha deta hai aur gumraahi mein woh unhi ko mubtala karta hai, jo fasik hain"
  2,27,"Allah ke ehad ko mazboot bandh lainay ke baad toar dete hain Allah ne jisay jornay ka hukum diya hai ussay kaat tay hain, aur zameen mein fasaad barpaa karte hain haqeeqat mein yahi log nuqsaan uthany walay hain"
  2,28,"tum Allah ke sath kufar ka rawayya kaisay ikhtiyar karte ho halaank tum bayjaan thay, is ne tum ko zindagi ataa ki, phir wohi tumhari jaan salb kere ga, phir wohi tumhe dobarah zindagi ataa kere ga, phir isi ki taraf tumhe palat kar jana hai"
  2,29,"wohi to hai, jis ne tumahray liye zameen ki saari cheeze peedakee, phir oopar ki taraf tavajja farmai aur saat aasman ustuwar kiye aur woh har cheez ka ilm rakhnay wala hai"
  2,30,"phir zara is waqt ka tasawwur karo jab tumahray Rab ne firshton se kaha tha ke"" Mein zameen mein aik khalifa bananay wala hon"" unhon ne arz kya :"" kya Aap zameen mein kisi aisay ko muqarar karne walay hain, jo is ke intizam ko bigaar day ga aur khonraziyan kere ga Aap ki hamd o Sana ke sath tasbeeh aur Aap ke liye taqdees to hum kar hi rahay hain"" farmaya :"" Mein jaanta hon jo kuch tum nahi jantay """
  2,31,"is ke baad Allah ne Aadam ko saari cheezon ke naam sikhayiye, phir inhen firshton ke samnay paish kya aur farmaya"" agar tumhara khayaal sahih hai ( ke kisi khalifa ke taqarrur se intizam baggar jaye ga ) to zara un cheezon ke naam batao """
  2,32,"unhon ne arz kya :"" nuqs se pak to Aap hi ki zaat hai, hum to bas itna hi ilm rakhtay hain, jitna Aap ne hum ko day diya hai haqeeqat mein sab kuch jan-nay aur samajhney wala Aap ke siwa koi nahi """
  2,33,"phir Allah ne Aadam se kaha :"" tum iِnhain inn cheezon ke naam batao"" jab is ne un ko unn sab ke naam bta diye, to Allah ne farmaya :"" Mein ne tum se kaha nah tha ke mein asmano aur zameen ki woh saari haqeqteen jaanta hon jo tum se makhfi hain, jo kuch tum zahir karte ho, woh bhi mujhe maloom hai aur jo kuch tum chupatay ho, usay bhi mein jaanta hon """
  2,34,"phir jab hum ne firshton ko hukum diya ke Aadam ke agay jhuk jao, to sab jhuk gay, magar iblees ne inkaar kya woh apni barayi ke ghamand mein par gaya aur na farmanoon mein shaamil ho gaya"
  2,35,"phir hum ne Aadam se kaha ke"" tum aur tumhari biwi, dono jannat mein raho aur yahan bafraghatjo chaho khao, magar is darakht ka rukh nah karna, warna zaalmon mein shumaar ho ge """
  2,36,"aakhir-kaar shetan ne un dono ko is darakht ki targheeb day kar hamaray hukum ki pairwi se hataa diya aur inhen uss haalat se nikalwa kar chorra, jis mein woh thay hum ne hukum diya ke,"" ab tum sab yahan se utar jao, tum aik dosray ke dushman ho aur tumhe aik khaas waqt taq zameen par therana thehrnaaur wahein guzar busr karna hai """
  2,37,"is waqt Aadam ne apne Rab se chund kalmaat seekh kar tauba ki, jis ko is ke Rab ne qubool kar liya, kyunkay woh bara maaf karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  2,38,"hum ne kaha ke,"" tum sab yahan se utar jao phir jo meri taraf se koi hadaayat tumahray paas puhanche, to jo log Merihadaayat ki pairwi karen ge, un ke liye kisi khauf aur ranj ka mauqa nah hoga"
  2,39,"aur jo is ko qubool karne se inkaar karen ge aur hamari ayaat ko jhutlain ge, woh aag mein jaane walay log hain, jahan woh hamesha rahen ge """
  2,40,"ae bani Israel ! zara khayaal karo meri is Nemat ka jo mein ne tum ko ataa ki thi, mere sath tumahra jo ehad tha ussay tum poora karo, to mera jo ehad tumahray sath tha ussay mein poora karoon ga aur mujh hi se tum daro"
  2,41,"aur mein ne jo kitaab bhaije hai is par imaan lao yeh uss kitaab ki taied mein hai jo tumahray paas pehlay se mojood thi, lehaza sab se pehlay tum hi is ke munkir nah ban jao thori qeemat par meri ayaat ko nah beech daalo aur mere ghazab se bachcho"
  2,42,baatil ka rang charha kar haq ko mushtaba nah banaao aur nah jantaybojhtay haq ko chupaney ki koshish karo
  2,43,"namaz qaim karo,zakat do aur jo log mere agay jhuk rahay hain unn ke sath tum bhi jhuk jao"
  2,44,"tum dosaron ko to neki ka rasta ikhtiyar karne ke liye kehte ho, magar apne aap ko bhool jatay ho? halaank tum kitaab ki talawat karte ho kya tum aqal se bilkul hi kaam nahi letay ?"
  2,45,"sabr aur namaz se madad lau, bay shak namaz aik sakht mushkil kaam hai"
  2,46,magar un farmaa bardaar bundon ke liye mushkil nahi hai jo samajte hain ke aakhir-kaar inhen apne Rab se milna aur isi ki taraf palat kar jana hai
  2,47,"ae bani Israel ! yaad karo meri uss Nemat ko, jis se mein ne tumhe nawaza tha aur is baat ko ke mein ne tumhe duniya ki saari qomon par fazeelat ataa ki thi"
  2,48,"aur daro uss din se jab koi kisi ke zara kaam nah aeye ga, nah kisi ki taraf se sifarish qubool hogi, nah kisi ko Fidya le kar chorra jaye ga, aur nah mujrimon ko kahin se madad mil sakay gi"
  2,49,"yaad karo woh waqt, jab hum ne tum ko firounion ki ghulami se nijaat bakhsh onhon ne tumhe sakht azaab mein mubtala kar rakha tha, tumahray larkoon ko zibah karte thay aur tumhari larkiyon ko zindah rehne dete thay aur is haalat mein tumahray Rab ki taraf se tumhari barri azmaish thi"
  2,50,"yaad karo woh waqt, jab hum ne samandar phaar kar tumahray liye rasta banaya, phir is mein se tumhe bakhariat guzaar diya, phir wahein tumhari aankhon ke samnay fironoon ko garqaab kiya"
  2,51,"yaad karo, jab hum ne( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)ko chalees Shabana roz ki qarardad par bulaya, to is ke peechay tum bichhre ko apna mabood bana baithy uss waqt tum ne barri zayad-ti ki thi"
  2,52,magar is par bhi Hum ne tumhe maaf kar diya ke shayad ab tum shukar guzaar bano
  2,53,yaad karo ke ( theek is waqt jab tum yeh zulm kar rahay thay ) hum ne( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)ko kitaab aur Farqan ataa ki taakay tum is ke zariye se seedha rasta pasko
  2,54,"yaad karo jab( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)( yeh Nemat letay hue palta, to uss ) ne apni qoum se kaha ke"" logo, tum ne bachhre ko mabood bana kar apne oopar sakht zulm kya hai, lehaza tum log apne khaaliq ke huzoor tauba karo aur apni jaanun ko halaak karo, isi mein tumahray khaaliq ke nazdeek tumhari behtari hai"" uss waqt tumahray khaaliq ne tumhari tauba qubool kar li ke woh bara maaf karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  2,55,"yaad karo jab tum ne( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)se kaha tha ke hum tumahray kehnay ka hargiz yaqeen nah karen ge, jab taq ke apni aankhon se alania khuda ko ( tum se kalaam karte ) nah dekh lain is waqt tumahray dekhte dekhte aik zabardast saiqayne tum ko aa liya"
  2,56,"tum bay- jaan ho kar gir chuke thay, magar phir hum ne tum ko(zindah kardiya) jِlaa uthaya, shayad ke is ahsaan ke baad tum shukar guzaar ban jao"
  2,57,"hum ne tum par abr ka saya kya, mann-o-salwa ki ghiza tumahray liye faraham ki aur tum se kaha ke jo pak cheeze hum ne tumhe bakhshi hain, unhen khao, magar tumahray islaaf ne jo kuch kya, woh hum par zulm nah tha, balkay unhon ne aap apne hi aap par zulm kya"
  2,58,"phir yaad karo jab hum ne kaha tha ke,"" yeh bastii jo tumahray samnay hai, is mein daakhil ho jao, is ki pedawar jis terhan chaho, mazay se khao, magar bastii ke darwazay mein sajda raiz hotay ho ye daakhil hona aur kehte jana hitta hitta , hum tumhari khataon se Dur guzar karen ge aur naiko karon ko mazeed fazl o karam se nawaazain ge """
  2,59,"magar jo baat kahi gayi thi, zaalmon ne ussay badal kar kuch aur kar diya aakhir-kaar hum ne zulm karne walon par aasman se azaab nazil kya yeh saza thi un nafarmanon ki, jo woh kar rahay thay"
  2,60,"yaad karo, jab( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)ne apni qoum ke liye pani ki dua ki to Hum ne kaha ke falan chattaan par apna asaa maro chunancha is se baara chashmay phoot niklay aur har qabeeley ne jaan liya ke konsi jagah is ke pani lainay ki hai uss waqt yeh hadaayat kar di gayi thi ke Allah ka diya howa rizaq khao piyo, aur zameen mein fasaad nah pheilatay phiro"
  2,61,"yaad karo, jab tum ne kaha tha ke,"" ae( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam), hum aik hi terhan ke khanay par sabr nahi kar saktay apne Rab se dua karo ke hamaray liye zameen ki pedawar saag, tarkari, kheera, kakri, gheehon, lahsun, pyaaz, daal waghera peda kere"" to( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)ne kaha :"" kya aik behtar cheez ke bajaye tum adna darjay ki cheeze laina chahtay ho? acha, kisi shehri abadi mein ja raho jo kuch tum mangte ho, wahan mil jaye ga"" aakhir-kaar nobat yahan taq pohanchi ke zillat o khawari aur pasti o bad haali unn par musallat ho gayi aur woh Allah ke ghazab mein ghir gay yeh nateeja tha is ka ke woh Allah ki ayaat se kufar karne lagey aur payghambaroon ko na-haq qatal karne lagey yeh nateeja tha un ki nafarmanyunka aur is baat ka ke woh hudood shara se nikal nikal jatay thay"
  2,62,"yaqeen jano ke nabi aRabi ko maan-ne walay hon ya yahodi, isaai hon ya Sabi , jo bhi Allah aur rozِ aakhir par imaan laaye ga aur naik amal kere ga, uss ka ajar is ke Rab ke paas hai aur is ke liye kisi khauf aur ranj ka mauqa nahi hai"
  2,63,"yaad karo woh waqt, jab hum ne tor ko tum par utha kar tum se pukhta ehad liya tha aur kaha tha ke"" jo kitaab hum tumhe day rahay hain usay mazbooti ke sath thamnaaur jo ehkaam o Hadayat is mein darj hain inhen yaad rakhna isi zariye se tawaqqa ki ja sakti hai ke tum taqwa ki rawish par chal saku ge """
  2,64,"magar is ke baad tum apne ehad se phِr gay is par bhi Allah ke fazl aur is ki rehmat ne tumhara sath nah chorra, warna tum kabhi ke tabah ho chuke hotay"
  2,65,phir tumhe apni qoum ke unn logon ka qissa to maloom hi hai jinhon ne sabt ka qanoon tora tha hum ne inhen keh diya ke bandar ban jao aur is haal mein raho ke har taraf se tum par dhutkar phatkaar parre
  2,66,is terhan hum ne unn ke injaam ko uss zamane ke logon aur baad ki anay wali naslon ke liye Ibrat aur darny walon ke liye nasihat bana kar chorra
  2,67,"phir woh waqea yaad karo, jab( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)ne apne qoum se kaha ke, Allah tumhe aik gaaye zibah karne ka hukum deta hai kehnay lagey kya tum hum se mazaq karte ho?( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)ne kaha, mein is se Khuda ki panah mangta hon ke jahilon ki si baatein karoon"
  2,68,"bolay acha, apne Rab se darkhwast karo ke woh hamein gaaye ki kuch tafseel betaye( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)ne kaha, Allah ka irshad hai ke woh aisi gaaye honi chahiye jo nah boorhi ho nah bachia, balkay ost Umar ki ho lehaza jo hukum diya jata hai is ki tameel karo"
  2,69,"phir kehnay lagey apne Rab se yeh aur pooch do ke uss ka rang kaisa ho( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)ne kaha woh farmata hai zard rang ki gaaye honi chahiye, jis ka rang aisa shokh ho ke dekhnay walon ka jee khush ho jaye"
  2,70,"phir bolay apne Rab se saaf saaf pooch kar batao kaisi gaaye matloob hai, hamein is ki taayun mein ishtibaah ho gaya hai Allah ne chaha, to hum is ka pata paleen ge"
  2,71,"( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)ne jawab diya : Allah kehta hai ke woh aisi gaaye hai jis se khidmat nahi li jati, nah zameenjotti hai nah pani khainchti hai, sahih salim aur bay daagh hai, is par woh pukaar utthay ke haan, ab tum ne theek pata bataya hai phir unhon ne usay zibah kya, warna woh aisa karte maloom nah hotay thay"
  2,72,"aur tumhe yaad hai woh waqea jab tum ne aik shakhs ki jaan li thi, phir is ke baray mein jhagrnay aur aik dosray par qatal ka ilzaam thopne lagey thay aur Allah ne faisla kar liya tha ke jo kuch tum chupatay ho, usay khol kar rakh day ga"
  2,73,uss waqt hum ne hukum diya ke maqtool ki laash ko is ke aik hissay se zarb lagao dekho is terhan Allah mُurdon ko zindagi bkhshta hai aur tumhe apni nishanain dekhata hai taakay tum samjhoo
  2,74,"magar aisi nishanain dekhnay ke baad bhi aakhir-kaar tumahray dil sakht hogaye, patharon ki taraf sakht, balkay sakhti mein kuch un se bhi barhay hue, kyunkay patharon mein se to koi aisa bhi hota hai jis mein se chashmay phoot bahtay hain, koi phutta hai aur is mein se pani nikal aata hai aur koi Khuda ke khauf se laraz kar gir bhi parta hai Allah tumahray kartoton se bay khabar nahi hai"
  2,75,ae muslmano! ab kya inn logon se tum yeh tawaqqa rakhtay ho ke tumhari dawat par imaan le ayen ge? halaank un mein se aik giroh ka Shewa yeh raha hai ke Allah ka kalaam suna aur phir khoob samajh boojh kar danista is mein tahreef ki
  2,76,"( Mohammad rasoolSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam par ) imaan laane walon se mlitay hain to kehte hain ke hum bhi inhen mantay hain, aur jab aapas mein aik dosray se takhliye ki baat cheet hoti hai to kehte hain ke bay waqoof hogaye ho? inn logon ko woh baatein batatay ho jo Allah ne tum par kholi hain taakay tumahray Rab ke paas tumahray muqablay mein inhen hujjat? mein paish karen"
  2,77,"aur kya yeh jantay nahi hain ke jo kuch yeh chupatay hain aur jo kuch zahir karte hain, Allah ko sab baton ki khabar hai"
  2,78,"un mein aik dosra giroh ummiyunka hai, jo kitaab ka to ilm rakhtay nahi, bas apni be bunyaad umedon aur aarzouon ko liye baithy hain aur mehez vahm o gumaan par chalay ja rahay hain"
  2,79,"pas halakat aur tabahi hai unn logon ke liye jo apne hathon se shara ka noshta likhte hain, phir logon se kehte hain ke yeh Allah ke paas se aaya howa hai taakay is ke muawzay mein thora sa faida haasil kar lain un ke hathon ka likha bhi un ke liye tabahi ka samaan hai aur un ki yeh kamaai bhi un ke liye mojab halakat"
  2,80,"woh kehte hain ke dozakh ki aag hamein hargiz chone wali nahi illa yeh ke chund roz ki sazamil jaye to mil jaye inn se pucho, kya tum ne Allah se koi ehad le liya hai, jis ki khilaaf warzi woh nahi karsaktha? ya baat yeh hai ke tum Allah ke zimmay daal kar aisi baatein keh dete ho jin ke mutaliq tumhe ilm nahi hai ke uss ne un ka zimma liya hai? aakhir tumhe dozakh ki aag kyun nah chovay gi ?"
  2,81,"jo bhi badi kamaye ga aur apni khata kaari ke chakkar mein para rahay ga, woh dozakhi hai aur dozakh hi mein woh hamesha rahay ga"
  2,82,aur jo log imaan layein ge aur naik amal karen ge wohi janati hain aur jannat mein woh hamesha rahen ge
  2,83,"yaad karo, Israel ki aulaad se Hum ne pukhta ehad liya tha ke Allah ke siwa kisi ki ibadat nah karna, maa baap ke sath, rishte daaron ke sath, yatimon aur miskeeno ke sath naik sulooq karna, logon se bhali baat kehna, namaz qaim karna aur zakat dena, magar thoray admion ke siwa ay tum sab is ehad se phir gay aur ab taq phiray hue ho"
  2,84,"phir zara yaad karo, Hum ne tum se mazboot ehad liya tha ke aapas mein aik dosray ka khoon nah bahana aur nah aik dosray ko ghar se bayghar karna tum ne is ka iqraar kya tha, tum khud is par gawah ho"
  2,85,"magar aaj wohi tum ho ke apne bhai bundon ko qatal karte ho, apni baradri ke kuch logon ko baykhanman kar dete ho, zulm o zayad-ti ke sath un ke khilaaf jathe bandiyan karte ho, aur jab woh larai mein pakrrae hue tumahray paas atay hain, to un ki rihayi ke liye Fidya ka lain deen karte ho, halaank inhen un ke gharon se nikalna hi suray se tum par haraam tha to kya tum kitaab ke aik hissay par imaan laatay ho aur dosray hissay ke sath kufar karte ho phir tum mein se jo log aisa karen, un ki saza is ke siwa aur kya hai ke duniya ki zindagi mein zaleel o khawar ho kar rahen aur akhirat mein shadeed tareen azaab ki taraf phair diye jayen? Allah un harkaat se bay khabar nahi hai, jo tum kar rahay ho"
  2,86,"yeh woh log hain jinhon ne akhirat beech kar duniya ki zindagi khareed li hai, lehaza nah inn ki saza mein koi takhfeef hogi aur nah inhen koi madad poanch sakay gi"
  2,87,"hum ne( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)ko kitaab di, is ke baad pay Dur pay rasool beje, aakhir-kaar ( hazrat ) Eesa Ibn maryam(alh-e-salam) ko roshan nishanain day kar bheja aur rooh pak se is ki madad ki phir yeh tumhara kya dhang hai ke jab bhi koi rasool tumhari khwahisaat nafs ke khilaaf koi cheez le kar tumahray paas aaya, to tum ne is ke muqablay mein sarkashi hi ki, kisi ko jhutlaya aur kisi ko qatal kar dala"
  2,88,"woh kehte hain, hamaray dil mehfooz hain,nahi, asal baat yeh hai ke un ke kufar ki wajah se un par Allah ki phutkaar pari hai, is liye woh kum hi imaan laatay hain"
  2,89,"aur ab jo aik kitaab Allah ki taraf se un ke paas aayi hai, is ke sath un ka kya bartao hai? bawajood yeh ke woh is kitaab ki tasdeeq karti hai jo un ke paas pehlay se mojo daal thi, bawajood yeh ke is ki aamad se pehlay woh khud kufar ke muqablay mein fatah o nusrat ki duayen manga karte thay, magar jab woh cheez aa gayi, jisay woh pehchan bhi gay to, unhon ne usay maan-ne se inkaar kar diya khuda ki laanat inn munkareen par"
  2,90,"kaisa bura zareya hai jis se yeh apne nafs ki tasalii haasil karte hain ke jo hadaayat Allah ne nazil ki hai, is ko qubool karne se sirf iss zid ki bana par inkaar kar rahay hain ke Allah ne apne fazl ( wahi o risalat ) se apne jis bande ko khud chaha, Nawaz diya! lehaza ab yeh ghazab baalaye ghazab ke mustahiq hogaye hain aur aisay kafiroon ke liye sakht aamaiz saza muqarrar hai"
  2,91,"jab unn se kaha jata hai ke jo kuch Allah ne nazil kya hai is par imaan lao, to woh kehte hain"" hum to sirf uss cheez par imaan laatay hain, jo hamaray haan ( yani nasal Israel ) mein utri hai"" is dairay ke bahir jo kuch aaya hai, usay maan-ne se woh inkaar karte hain, halaank woh haq hai aur uss taleem ki tasdeeq o taied kar raha hai jo un ke haan pehlay se mojood thi acha, un se kaho : agar tum is taleem hi par imaan rakhnay walay ho jo tumahray haan aayi thi, to is se pehlay Allah ke unn payghambaroon ko ( jo khud bani Israel mein peda hue thay ) kyun qatal karte rahay ?"
  2,92,tumahray paas( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)kaisi kaisi roshan nshanyon ke sath aaya phir bhi tum aisay zalim thay ke is ke peeth morty hi bichhre ko mabood bana baithy
  2,93,"phir zara uss mesaq ko yaad karo, jo tor ko tumahray oopar utha kar Hum ne tum se liya tha Hum ne takeed ki thi ke jo Hadayat Hum day rahay hain, un ki sakhti ke sath pabandi karo aur kaan laga kar suno tumahray islaaf ne kaha ke hum ne sun liya, magar manen ge nahi aur un ki baatil parasti ka yeh haal tha ke dilon mein un ke bitchrha hi basa howa tha kaho : agar tum momin ho, to ajeeb imaan hai, jo aisi buri harkaat ka tumhe hukum deta hai"
  2,94,"inn se kaho ke agar waqai Allah ke nazdeek akhirat ka ghar tamam insanon ko chore kar sirf tumahray hi liye makhsoos hai, tab to tumhe chahiye ke mout ki tamanna karo, agar tum apne is khayaal mein sachey ho"
  2,95,"yaqeen jano ke yeh kabhi is ki tamanna nah karen ge, is liye ke apne hathon jo kuch kama kar unhon ne wahan bheja hai, is ka iqtiza yahi hai ( ke yeh wahan jaane ki tamanna nah karen ) Allah un zaalmon ke haal se khoob waaqif hai"
  2,96,"tum inhen sab se barh kar jeeney ka harees pao ge hatta ke yeh is muamlay mein mushrikon se bhi barhay hue hain un mein se aik aik shakhs yeh chahta hai ke kisi terhan hazaar baras jie, halaank lambi Umar behar haal ussay azaab se to daur nahi pheink sakti jaisay kuch aamaal yeh kar rahay hain, Allah to inhen dekh hi raha hai"
  2,97,"inn se kaho ke jo koi Jibreel se adawat rakhta ho, usay maloom hona chahiye ke Jibreel ne Allah ke azan se yeh quran tumahray qalb par nazil kya hai, jo pehlay aayi hui kitabon ki tasdeeq o taied karta hai aur imaan laane walon ke liye hadaayat aur kamyabi ki basharat ban kar aaya hai"
  2,98,"( agar Jibreel se un ki adawat ka sabab yahi hai, to keh do ke ) jo Allah aur is ke firshton aur is ke rasolon Rasolo-n aur Jibreel aur mikaeel ke dushman hain, Allah un kafiroon ka dushman hai"
  2,99,"hum ne tumhari taraf aisi ayaat nazil ki hain jo saaf saaf haq ka izhaar kar ne wali hain aur un ki pairwi se sirf wohi log inkaar karte hain, jo fasik hain"
  2,100,"kya hamesha aisa hi nahi hota raha hai ke jab unhon ne koi ehad kya, to un mein se aik nah aik giroh ne usay zaroor hi baala ye taaq rakh diya? balkay un mein se aksar aisay hi hain, jo sachey dil se imaan nahi laatay"
  2,101,"aur jab un ke paas Allah ki taraf se koi rasool is kitaab ki tasdeeq o taied karta howa aaya jo un ke haan pehlay se mojood thi, to inn ahal kitaab mein se aik giroh ne kitaab Allah ko is terhan pas pusht dala, goya ke woh kuch jantay hi nahi"
  2,102,"aur lagey unn cheezon ki pairwi karne, jo shiyateen , sulaiman ki saltanat ka naam le kar paish kya karte thay, halaank sulaiman ne kabhi kufar nahi kya, kufar ke murtakib to woh shyatin thay jo logon ko jaadoo giri ki taleem dete thay woh peechay parre uss cheez ke jo babul mein do firshton, harwat o Maruat par nazil ki gayi thi, halaank woh ( farishtay ) jab bhi kisi ko is ki taleem dete thay, to pehlay saaf tor par mutnabba kar diya karte thay ke"" dekh, hum mehez aik azmaish hain, to kufar mein mubtala nah ho"" phir bhi yeh log unn se woh cheez sikhte thay, jis se shohar aur biwi mein judai daal den zahir tha ke azan Ellahi ke baghair woh is zariye se kisi ko bhi zarrar nah pouncha satke thay, mgras ke bawajood woh aisi cheez sikhte thay jo khud un ke liye naffa bakhash nahi, balkay nuqsaan daal hay thi aur inhen khoob maloom tha ke jo is cheez ka khredar bana, is ke liye akhirat mein koi hissa nahi kitni buri mata thi jis ke badlay unhon ne apni jaanun ko beech dala, kash inhen maloom hota !"
  2,103,"agar woh imaan aur taqwa ikhtiyar karte, to Allah ke haan is ka jo badla milta, woh un ke liye ziyada behtar tha, kash unhen khabar hoti"
  2,104,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho : ra-ana nah kaha karo, balkay anzarna kaho aur tavajja se baat ko suno, yeh kafir to azaab alim ke mustahiq hain"
  2,105,"yeh log jinhon ne dawat haq ko qubool karne se inkaar kar diya hai, khuwa ahal kitaab mein se hon ya mushriq hon, hargiz yeh pasand nahi karte ke tumahray Rab ki taraf se tum par koi bhalai nazil ho, magar Allah jis ko chahta hai, apni rehmat ke liye chunn laita hai aur woh bara fazl frmane wala hai"
  2,106,"hum apni jis aayat ko mansookh kar dete hain ya bُhla dete hain, is ki jagah is se behtar le atay hain ya kam az kam waisi hi kya tum jantay nahi ho ke Allah har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai ?"
  2,107,kya tumhe khabar nahi hai ke zamee aur aasman ki farmanrawai Allah hi ke liye hai aur is ke siwa koi tumhari khabar Gary karne aur tumhari madad karne wala nahi hai ?
  2,108,"phir kya tum apne rasool se is qisam ke sawalaat aur mutalba karna chahtay ho, jaisay is se pehlay( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)se kiye ja chuke hain? halaank jis shakhs ne imaan ki rawish ko kufar ki rawish se badal liya woh raah raast se bhatak gaya"
  2,109,"ahal kitaab mein se aksar log yeh chahtay hain ke kisi terhan tumhe imaan se phair kar phir kufar ki taraf palta le jayen agarchay haq un par zahir ho chuka hai, magar apne nafs ke hasad ki bana par tumahray liye un ki yeh khwahish hai is ke jawab mein tum Afoo o Dur guzar se kaam lau yahan taq ke Allah khud hi apna faisla nafiz kar day mutmaen raho ke Allah taala har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
  2,110,"namaz qaim karo aurzakat do tum apni aqibat ke liye jo bhalai kama kar agay bhaijho ge, Allah ke haan usay mojood pao ge jo kuch tum karte ho, woh sab Allah ki nazar mein hai"
  2,111,"un ka kehna hai ke koi shakhs jannat mein nah jaye ga jab taq ke woh yahodi nah ho ( ya esaion ke khayaal ke mutabiq ) isaai nah ho yeh un ki tamannaye hain un se kaho, apni Daleel paish karo, agar tum apne daaway mein sachey ho"
  2,112,"darasal nah tumhari kuch khasusiyat hai, nah kisi aur ki haq yeh hai ke jo bhi apni hasti ko Allah ki itaat mein saump day aur amlan naik rawish par chalay, is ke liye is ke Rab ke paas uss ka ajar hai aur aisay logon ke liye kisi khauf ya ranj ka koi mauqa nahi"
  2,113,"yahodi kehte hain : esaion ke paas kuch nahi isaai kehte hain : yahudion ke paas kuch nahi halaank dono hi kitaab parhte hain aur isi qisam ke daaway un logon ke bhi hain, jin ke paas kitaab ka ilm nahi hai yeh ikhtilafat jin mein yeh log mubtala hain, un ka faisla Allah qayamat ke roz kar day ga"
  2,114,"aur iss shakhs se barh kar zalim kon hoga jo Allah ke m'abodoomein is ke naam ki yaad se rokay aur un ki weerani ke darpay ho? aisay log is qabil hain ke un ki ibadat gaahon mein qadam nah rakhen aur agar wahan jayen bhi, to drtay hue jayen un ke liye to duniya mein ruswai hai aur akhirat mein azaab azeem"
  2,115,"mashriq aur maghrib sab Allah ke hain jis taraf bhi tum rukh karo ge, isi taraf Allah ka rukh hai Allah barri wusat wala aur sab kuch jan-nay wala hai"
  2,116,"un ka qoul hai ke Allah ne kisi ko beta banaya hai Allah pak hai un baton se asal haqeeqat yeh hai ke zameen aur asmano ki tamam mojoodaat is ki malik hain, sab ke sab is ke Mutee farmaan hain"
  2,117,"woh asmano aur zameen ka mo-jad hai aur jis baat ka woh faisla karta hai, is ke liye bas yeh hukum deta hai ke"" ho ja"" aur woh ho jati hai"
  2,118,nadaan kehte hain ke Allah khud hum se baat kyun nahi karta ya koi nishani hamaray paas kyun nahi aati? aisi hi baatein inn se pehlay log bhi kya karte thay inn sab ( aglay pichlle gumrahon ) ki ذہنیتیں aik jaisi hain yaqeen laane walon ke liye to hum nishanain saaf saaf numaya kar chuke hain
  2,119,"( is se barh kar nishani kya hogi ke ) hum ne tum ko ilm haq ke sath khush khaberi dainay wala war darane wala bana kar bheja ab jo log jahannum se rishta joor chuke hain, un ki taraf se tum zimma daar o jawab da nahi ho"
  2,120,"yahodi aur isaai tum se hargiz raazi nah hon ge, jab taq tum un ke tareeqay par nah chalne lagu saaf keh do keh rasta bas wohi hai, jo Allah ne bataya hai warna agras ilm ke baad, jo tumahray paas aa chuka hai, tum ne unn ki khwahisaat ki pairwi ki, to Allah ki pakar se bachanay wala koi dost aur madad gaar tumahray liye nahi hai"
  2,121,"jin logon ko hum ne kitaab di hai, woh ussay is terhan parhte hain jaissa ke parhnay ka haq hai woh is par sachey dil se imaan laatay hain aur jwas ke sath kufar ka rawayya ikhtiyar karen, wohi asal mein nuqsaan uthany walay hain"
  2,122,"ae bani Israel ! yaad karo meri woh Nemat , jis se mein ne tumhe Nawaz a tha, aur yeh ke mein ne tumhe duniya ki tamam qomon par fazeelat di thi"
  2,123,"aur daro uss din se, jab koi kisi ke zara kaam nah aeye ga, nah kisi se Fidya qubool kya jaye ga, nah koi sifarish hi aadmi ko faida day gi, aur nah mujrimon ko kahin se koi madad poanch sakay gi"
  2,124,"yaad karo ke jab ibrahim ko is ke Rab ne chand baton mein aazma ya aur woh unn sab mein poora utar gaya, to is ne kaha :"" mein tujhe sab logon ka peshwa bananay wala hon"" ibrahim ne arz kya :"" aur kya meri aulaad se bhi yahi wada hai ?"" is ne jawab diya :"" mera wada zaalmon se mutaliq nahi hai """
  2,125,aur yeh ke hum ne is ghar ( kaabay ) ko logon ke liye markaz aur aman ki jagah qarar diya tha aur logon ko hukum diya tha ke ibrahim jahan ibadat ke liye khara hota hai is maqam ko mustaqil jaye namaz bana lau aur ibrahim aur Ismailko takeed ki thi ke mere ghar ko tuwaf aur aitekaf aur ruku aur sajda karne walon ke liye pak rakho
  2,126,"aur yeh ke ibrahim ne dua ki :"" ae mere Rab, is shehar ko aman ka shehar bana day, aur is ke bashindon mein jo Allah aur akhirat ko manen, inhen har qisam ke phalon ka rizaq day"" jawab mein is ke Rab ne farmaya :"" aur jo nah manay ga, duniya ki chand roza zindagi ka samaan to mein ussay bhi dun ga magar aakhir kaar ussay azaab jahannum ki taraf ghsitoonga, aur woh bad tareen thikana hai """
  2,127,"aur yaad karo ibrahim aur asmayl jab is ghar ki diivaaren utha rahay thay, to dua karte jatay thay :"" ae hamaray Rab, hum se yeh khidmat qubool farma le, to sab ki suneney aur sab kuch jan-nay wala hai"
  2,128,"ae Rab, hum dono ko apna muslim ( mutee farmaan ) bana, hamari nasal se aik aisi qoum utha, jo teri muslim ho, hamein apni ibadat ke tareeqay bta, aur hamari kotahyon se Dur guzar farma, to bara maaf karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  2,129,"aur ae Rab, un logon mein khud inhen ki qoum se aik aisa rasool utha وjo inhen teri ayaat sunaye, un ko kitaab aur hikmat ki taleem day aur un ki zindaganian sanware to bara muqtadir aur hakeem hai """
  2,130,"ab kon hai, jo ibrahim ke tareeqay se nafrat kere? jis ne khud apne aap ko hamaqat o jahalat mein mubtala kar liya ho, is ke so a kon yeh harkat karsaktha hai? ibrahim to woh shakhs hai, jis ko hum ne duniya mein apne kaam ke liye chuun liya tha aur akhirat mein is ka shumaar saliheenmein hoga"
  2,131,"is ka haal yeh tha ke jab is ke Rab ne is se kaha :"" muslim ho ja "", to is ne foran kaha :"" mein maalik kaayenaat ka"" muslim"" ho gaya """
  2,132,"isi tareeqay par chalne ki hadaayat is ne apni aulaad ko ki thi aur isi ki wasiyat yaqoob apni aulaad ko kar gaya is ne kaha tha ke :"" mere bachcho! Allah ne tumahray liye yahi deen pasand kya hai lehaza martay dam taq muslim hi rehna """
  2,133,"phir kya tum is waqt mojood thay, jab yaqoob is duniya se rukhsat ho raha tha? is ne martay waqt apne bachon se poocha :"" bachcho! mere baad tum kis ki bandagi karo ge ?"" un sab ne jawab diya :"" hum isi aik khuda ki bandagi karen ge jisay aap ne aur aap ke buzurgon ibrahim, Ismael aur ishaq ne khuda maana hai aur hum usi ke muslim hain """
  2,134,"woh kuch log thay, jo guzar gay jo kuch unhon ne kamaya, woh unn ke liye hai aur jo kuch tum kamao ge, woh tumahray liye hai tum se yeh nah poocha jaye ga ke woh kya karte thay"
  2,135,"yahodi kehte hain : yahodi ho to raah raast pao ge isaai kehte hain : isaai ho, to hadaayat miley gi inn se kaho :"" nahi, balkay sab ko chore kar ibrahim ka tareeqa aur ibrahim mshr ko n mein se nah tha """
  2,136,"muslmano! kaho ke :"" hum imaan laaye Allah par aur is hadaayat par jo hamari taraf nazil hui hai aur jo ibrahim, Ismael, ishaq, yaqoob aur aulaad yaqoob ki taraf nazil hui thi aur jo( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)aur eesa aur dosray tamam payghambaroon ko unn ke Rab ki taraf se di gayi thi hum un ke darmain koi tafreeq nahi karte aur hum Allah ke muslim hain """
  2,137,"phir agar woh usi terhan imaan layein, jis terhan tum laaye ho, to hadaayat par hain, aur agras se mun phairen, to khuli baat hai ke woh hatt dharmi mein par gay hain lehaza itminan rakho ke unn ke muqablay mein Allah tumhari himayat ke liye kaafi hai woh sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai"
  2,138,"kaho :"" Allah ka rang ikhtiyar karo is ke rang se acha aur kis ka rang hoga? aur hum usi ki bandagi karne walay log hain """
  2,139,"aeNabi NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ! inn se kaho :"" kya tum Allah ke baray mein hum se jhagarte ho? halaank wohi hamara Rab bhi hai aur tumhara Rab bhi hamaray aamaal hamaray liye hain, tumahray aamaal tumahray liye, aur hum Allah hi ke liye apni bandagi ko khalis kar chuke hain"
  2,140,"ya phir kya tma ra kehna yeh hai ke ibrahim, Ismael, ishaq, yaqoob aur aulaad yaqoob sab ke sab yahodi thay ya nasrani thay? kaho :"" tum ziyada jantay ho ya Allah ? uss shakhs se bara zalim aur kon hoga jis ke zimmay Allah ki taraf se aik gawahi ho aur woh ussay chupaye? tumhari harkaat se Allah ghaafil to nahi hai"
  2,141,"woh kuch log thay, jo guzar chuke unn ki kamaai unn ke liye thi aur tumhari kamaai tumahray liye tum se unn ke aamaal ke mutaliq sawal nahi hoga """
  2,142,"nadaan log zaroor kahin ge : aِnhin kya howa ke pehlay yeh jis qble ki taraf rukh kar ke namaz parhte thay, is se yakayak phir gay? ae nabi, un se kaho :"" mashriq aur maghrib sab Allah ke hain Allah jisay chahta hai, seedhi raah dikha deta hai"
  2,143,"aur isi terhan to hum ne tumhe aik"" ummat wast"" banaya hai taakay tum duniya ke logon par gawah ho aur rasool tum par gawah ho pehlay jis taraf tum rukh karte thay, is ko to hum ne sirf yeh dekhnay ke liye qibla muqarrar kya tha ke kon rasool ki pairwi karta hai aur kon ulta phir jata hai yeh maamla tha to bara sakht, magar unn logon ke liye kuch bhi sakht nah saabit howa, jo Allah ki hadaayat se Faiz yab thay Allah tumahray is imaan ko hargiz zaya nah kere ga, yaqeen jano ke woh logon ke haq mein nihayat shafeeq o Raheem hai"
  2,144,"yeh tumahray mun ka baar baar aasman ki taraf uthna hum dekh rahay hain lau, hum usi qble ki taraf tumhe phairay dete hain, jisay tum pasand karte ho masjid haraam ki taraf rukh phair do ab jahan kahin tum ho, usi ki taraf munh kar ke namaz parha karo yeh log jinheinkitaab di gayi thi, khoob jantay hain ke ( tehweel qibla ka ) yeh hukum un ke Rab hi ki taraf se hai aur Bar haq hai, mgra iske bawajood jo kuch yeh kar rahay hain, Allah is se ghaafil nahi hai"
  2,145,"tum un ahal kitaab ke paas khuwa koi nishani le aao, mumkin nahi ke yeh tumahray qble ki pairwi karne lagen, aur nah tumahray liye yeh mumkin hai ke un ke qble ki pairwi karo, aur un mein se koi giroh bhi dosray ke qble ki pairwi ke liye tayyar nahi hai, o ray agar tum ne is ilm ke baad jo tumahray paas aa chuka hai, un ki khwahisaat ki pairwi ki, to yaqeenan tumhara shumaar zaalmon mein hoga"
  2,146,"jin logon ko hum ne kitaab di hai, woh iss maqam ko ( jisay qibla banaya gaya hai ) aisa pehchante hain, jaissa apni aulaad ko pehchante hain magar un mein se aik giroh jantay bojhtay haq ko chhupa raha hai"
  2,147,"yeh qatee aik amar haq hai tumahray Rab ki taraf se, lehaza is ke mutaliq tum hargiz kisi shak mein nah parro"
  2,148,"har aik ke liye aik rukh hai, jis ki taraf woh mrhta hai pas bhala ئیوں ki taraf Sabqat karo jahan bhi tum ho ge, Allah tumhe pa le ga uss ki qudrat se koi cheez bahar nahi"
  2,149,"tumhara guzar jis maqam se bhi ho, wahein apna rukh ( namaz ke waqt ) masjid haraam ki taraf phair do, kyunkay yeh tumahray Rab ka bilkul haq faisla hai aur Allah tum logon ke aamaal se bay khabar nahi hai"
  2,150,"aur jahan se bhi tumhara guzar ho, apna rukh masjid haraam ki taraf phera karo, aur jahan bhi tum ho, usi ki taraf mun kar ke numa zay parho taakay logon ko tumahray khilaaf koi Hujjat nah miley haan jo zalim hain, unn ki zabaan kisi haal mein band nah hogi to unn se tum nah daro, balkay mujh se daro aur is liye ke mein tum par apni Nemat poori kar dun aur is tawaqqa par ke mere is hukum ki pairwi se tum isi terhan Falah ka rasta pao ge"
  2,151,"jis terhan ( tumhe iss cheez se Falah naseeb hui ke ) mein ne tumahray darmain khud tum mein se aik rasool bheja, jo tumhe meri ayaat sunataa hai, tumhari zindagion ko sanwarta hai, tumhe kitaab aur hikmat ki taleem deta hai, aur tumhe woh baatein sakata hai, jo tum nah jantay thay"
  2,152,"lehaza tum mujhe yaad rakho, mein tumhe yaad rakhon ga aur mera shukar ada karo, kufran Nemat nah karo"
  2,153,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, sabr aur namaz se madad lau Allah sabr karne walon ke sath hai"
  2,154,"aur jo log Allah ki raah mein maaray jayen, inhen murda nah kaho, aisay log to haqeeqat mein zindah hain, magar tumhe un ki zindagi ka shaoor nahi hota"
  2,155,"aur hum zaroor tumhe khauf o khatar, faqa kashi, jaan o maal ke nuqsanaat aur aamdnyon ke ghatay mein mubtala kar ke tumhari azmaish karen ge"
  2,156,"inn halaat mein jo log sabr karen aur jab koi museebat parre, to kahin ke :"" hum Allah hi ke hain aur Allah hi ki taraf hamein palat kar jana hai """
  2,157,"inhen khush khaberi day do un par un ke Rab ki taraf se barri inayaat hon gi, uss ki rehmat unn par saya kere gi aur aisay hi log raast ro hain"
  2,158,"yaqeenan Safa aur marwah, Allah ki nshanyon mein se hain lehaza jo shakhs beeet Allah ka hajj ya omra kere, is ke liye koi gunah ki baat nahi ke woh inn dono pahariyoon ke darmain sae kar le aur jo brza o raghbat koi bhalai ka kaam kere ga, Allah ko is ka ilm hai o ray woh is ki qader karne wala hai"
  2,159,"jo log hamari nazil ki hui roshan talemaat aur Hadayat ko chupatay hain,dar-aa-n hala-n kehہ hum inhen sab insanon ki rahnumai ke liye apni kitaab mein bayan kar chuke hain, yaqeen jano ke Allah bhi un par laanat karta hai aur tamam laanat karne walay bhi unn par laanat bhaijtay hain"
  2,160,"Albata jo is rawish se baz aa jayen aur apne tarz amal ki islaah kar lain aur jo kuch chupatay thay, ussay bayan karne lagen, unn ko mein maaf kar dun ga aur mein bara Dur guzar karne wala aur reham karne wala hon"
  2,161,"jin logon ne kufar ka rawayya ikhtiyar kya aur kufar ki haalat hi mein jaan di, un par Allah aur firshton aur tamam insanon ki laanat hai"
  2,162,"isi laanat zadgi ki haalat mein woh hamesha rahen ge, nah unn ki sz amin takhfeef hogi aur nah inhen phir koi doosri mohlat di jaye gi"
  2,163,"tumhara khuda aik hi khuda hai, uss Rehman aur Raheem ke siwa koi aur khuda nahi hai"
  2,164,"( iss haqeeqat ko pehchanney ke liye agar koi nishani aur alamat drka rahay to ) jo log aqal se kaam letay hain unn ke liye asmano aur zameen ki saakht mein, raat aur din ke pihm aik dosray ke baad anay mein, unn kashtiyon mein juaa nsan ke naffa ki cheeze liye hue daryaaon aur samndron mein chalti phurti hain, barish ke uss pani mein jisay Allah oopar se brsata hai phir is ke zariye se zameen ko zindagi bkhshta hai aur apne isi intizam ki badolat zameen mein har qisam ki jaan daar makhlooq phelata hai, hawaon ki gardish mein, aur unn baadalon mein jo aasman aur zameen ke darmain tabay farmaan bana kar rakhay gay hain, be shumaar nishanain hain"
  2,165,"( magar wahdat khuda wandi par Dalalat karne walay inn khulay khulay assaar ke hotay hue bhi ) kuch log aisay hain jo Allah ke siwa dosaron ko is ka humsar aur mad-muqabil banatay hain aur unn ke aisay garweedah hain jaisay Allah ke sath garweed-gi honi chahiye halaank imaan rakhnay walay log sab se barh kar Allah ko mehboob rakhtay hain kash, jo kuch azaab ko samnay dekh kar inhen sojhnaywala hai woh aaj hi inn zaalmon ko soojh jaye ke saari taqtin aur saaray ikhtiyarat Allah hi ke qabzay mein hain aur yeh ke Allah saza dainay mein bhi bohat sakht hai"
  2,166,"jab woh saza day ga is waqt kefiyat yeh hogi ke wohi peshwa aur rehnuma, jin ki duniya mein pairwi ki gayi thi, apne pairwon se be taulqi zahir karen ge, magar saza pa kar rahen ge aur un ke saaray asbaab o wasail ka silsila kat jaye ga"
  2,167,"aur woh log jo duniya mein unn ki pairwi karte thay, kahin ge ke kash hum ko phir aik mauqa diya jata to jis terhan aaj yeh hum se bezari zahir kar rahay hain, hum inn se bezaar ho kar dikha dete yun Allah inn logon ke woh aamaal jo yeh duniya mein kar rahay hain, un ke samnay iss terhan laaye ga ke yeh hasratoon aurpashaymaniyunke sath haath mlitay rahen ge magar aag se niklny ki koi raah nah payen ge"
  2,168,logo! zameen mein jo halal aur pak cheeze hain inhen khao aur shetan ke betaye hue raastoon par nah chalo woh tumhara khula dushman hai
  2,169,tumhe badi aur fehash ka hukum deta hai aur yeh sakata hai ke tum Allah ke naam par woh baatein kaho jin ke mutaliq tumhe ilm nahi hai ke woh Allah ne farmai hain
  2,170,un se jab kaha jata hai ke Allah ne jo ehkaam nazil kiye hain unn ki pairwi karo to jawab dete hain ke hum to isi tareeqay ki pairwi karen ge jis par hum ne apne baap dada ko paaya hai acha agar un ke baap dada ne aqal se kuch bhi kaam nah liya ho aur raah raast nah payi ho to kya phir bhi yeh inhen ki pairwi kiye chalay jayen ge ?
  2,171,"yeh log jinhon ne khuda ke betaye hue tareeqay par chalne se inkaar kar diya hai inn ki haalat bilkul aisi hai jaisay charwaha janwaron ko pukaarta hai aur woh haank pukaar ki sada ke siwa kuch nahi suntay yeh behray hain, gungay hain, andhay hain, is liye koi baat un ki samajh mein nahi aati"
  2,172,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, agar tum haqeeqat mein Allah ki bandagi karne walay ho to jo pak cheeze hum ne tumhe bakhsh hain unhen be takalouf khao aur Allah ka shukar ada karo"
  2,173,"Allah ki taraf se agar koi pabandi tum par hai to woh yeh hai ke Murdaar nah khao, khoon se aur soor ke gosht se parhaiz karo aur koi cheez nah khao jis par Allah ke siwa kisi aur ka naam liya gaya ho haan jo shakhs majaboori ki haalat mein ho aur woh un mein se koi cheez kha le baghair is ke ke woh qanoon shikni ka iradah rakhta ho ya zaroorat ki hadd se tajawaz kar y, to is par kuch gunah nahi, Allah bakhsnay wala aur reham karne wala hai"
  2,174,"haq yeh hai ke jo log unn ehkaam ko chupatay hain jo Allah ne apni kitaab mein naz l- kiye hain aur thoray se dunewi faido para nahi bhaint charhatay hain, woh darasal apne pait aag se bhar rahay hain qayamat ke roz Allah hargiz un se baat nah kere ga, nah unhen pakeeza tehra-ay ga, aur unn ke liye dard naak saza hai"
  2,175,yeh woh log hain jinhon ne hadaayat ke badlay zala-lat khareedi aur mughfirat ke badlay azaab mol le liya kaisa ajeeb hai un ka hosla ke jahannum ka azaab bardasht karne ke liye tayyar hain
  2,176,yeh sab kuch is wajah se howa ke Allah ne to theek theek haq ke mutabiq kitaab nazil ki thi magar jin logon ne kitaab mein ikhtilaaf nikalay woh apne jhagron mein haq se bohat daur nikal gay
  2,177,"neki yeh nahi hai ke tum ne apne chehray mashriq ki taraf kar liye ya maghrib ki taraf, balkay neki yeh hai ke aadmi Allah ko aur yom aakhir aur mulaika ko aur Allah ki nazil ki hui kitaab aur is ke payghambaroon ko dil se manay aur Allah ki mohabbat mein apna dil pasand maal rishte daaron aur yatimon par, miskeeno aur musafroon par, madad ke liye haath phelanay walon par aur ghulamoon ki rihayi par kharch kere, namaz qaim kere aurzakat day aur naik woh log hain ke jab ehad karen to ussay wafa karen, aur tangi o museebat ke waqt mein aur haq o baatil ki jung mein sabr karen yeh hainrasbaaz log aur yahi log mut-taqi hain"
  2,178,"a y logo jo imaan laaye ho, tumahray liye qatal ke mqdmon mein qisaas ka hukum likh diya gaya hai azad aadmi ne qatal kya ho to is azad hi se badla liya jaye, ghulam qaatil ho to woh ghulam hi qatal kya jaye, aur aurat iss jurm ki murtakib ho tawa seen aurat hi se qisaas liya jaye haan agar kisi qaatil ke sath is ka bhai kuch narmi karne ke liye tayyar ho, to Maroof tareeqay ke mutabiq khoo baha ka tasfia hona chahiye aur qaatil ko lazim hai ke raasti ke sath khoo baha ada kere yeh tumahray Rab ki taraf se takhfeef aur rehmat hai is par bhi jo zayad-ti kere, is ke liye dard naak saza hai"
  2,179,aqal o khiirad rakhnay walo! tumahray liye qisaas mein zindagi hai umeed hai ke tum is qanoon ki khilaaf warzi se parhaiz karo ge
  2,180,"tum par farz kya gaya hai ke jab tum mein se kisi ki mout ka waqt aeye aur woh apne peechay maal chore raha ho, to walidain aur rishta daaron ke liye Maroof tareeqay se wasiyat kere yeh haq hai mut-taqi logon par"
  2,181,"phir jinhon ne wasiyat suni aur baad mein ussay badal dala, tawa seen ka gunah un badalny walon par hoga Allah sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai"
  2,182,"Albata jis ko yeh andesha ho ke wasiyat karne walay ne na danista ya qasdan haq talfi ki hai, aur phir muamlay se talluq rakhnay walon ke darmain woh islaah kere, to is par kuch gunah nahi hai, Allah bakhsnay wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  2,183,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, tum par rozay farz kar diye gay, jis terhan tum se pehlay Anabia ke پیروؤں par farz kiye gay thay is se tawaqqa hai ke tum mein taqwa ki sift peda hogi"
  2,184,"chand muqarrar dinon ke rozay hain agar tum mein se koi bemaar ho, ya safar par ho to dosray dinon mein itni hi tadaad poori kar le aur jo log roza rakhnay ki qudrat rakhtay hon ( phir nah rakhen ) to woh Fidya den aik rozay ka Fidya aik maskeen ko khana khilana hai aur jo apni khusi se kuch ziyada bhalai kere to yeh isi ke liye behtar hai lekin agar tum samjhoo, to tumahray haq mein acha yahi hai ke roza rakho"
  2,185,"ramadaan woh maheena hai, jis mein quran nazil kya gaya jo insanon ke liye sara sar hadaayat hai aur aisi wazeh talemaat par mushtamil hai, jo raah raast dikhaane wali aur haq o baatil ka farq khol kar rakh dainay wali hain lehaza ab se jo shakhs is mahinay ko paye, uss ko lazim hai ke iss poooray mahinay ke rozay rakhay aur jo koi mareez ho ya safar par ho, to woh dosray dinon mein rozon ki tadaad poori kere Allah tumahray sath narmi karna chahta hai, sakhti karna nahi chahta is liye yeh tareeqa tumhe bataya ja raha hai taakay tum rozon ki tadaad poori krsko aur jis hadaayat se Allah ne tumhe Sarfraz kya hai, uss par Allah ki kibriya yi ka izhaar o aitraaf karo aur shukar guzaar bano"
  2,186,"aur ae NabiNabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallammere bande agar tum se mere mutaliq poucheen, to unhen bta do ke mein un se qareeb hi hon pukarnay wala jab mujhe pukaarta hai, mein uss ki pukaar santa aur jawab deta hon lehaza inhen chahiye ke meri dawat par labaik kahin aur mujh par imaan layein yeh baat tum unhen suna do, shayad ke woh raah raast paleen"
  2,187,"tumahray liye rozon ke zamane mein raton ko apni biwion ke paas jana halal kar diya gaya hai woh tumahray liye libaas hain aur tum unn ke liye Allah ko maloom ho gaya ke tum log chupkay chupkay apne aap se khayanat kar rahay thay, magar aُ seen ne tumhara qasoor maaf kar diya aur tum se dar guzar farmaya ab tum apni biwion ke sath shab bashi karo aur jo lutaf Allah ne tumahray liye jaaiz kar diya hai, ussay haasil karo neez raton ko khao piyo yahan taq ke tum ko siyahi shab ki dahari sesupaidah سپیدۂ subah ki dahari numaya nazar aa jaye tab yeh sab kaam chore kar raat taq apna roza poora karo aur jab tum masjidoon meinmo'a-takifho, to biwion se mubashrat nah karo yeh Allah ki baandhi hui hade hain, un ke qareeb nah phatakna iss terhan Allah apne ehkaam logon ke liye Busrahat bayan karta hai, tawaqqa hai ke woh ghalat ravayye se bachchen ge"
  2,188,aur tum log nah to aapas mein aik dosray ke maal naarwa tareeqa se khao aur nah hakmon ke agay un ko is gharz ke liye paish karo ke tumhe dosaron ke maal ka koi hissa qasdan zalimana tareeqay se khanay ka mauqa mil jaye
  2,189,log tum se chaand ki ghatti barhti sooraton ke mutaliq puchhte hain kaho : yeh logon ke liye tarikhon ki taayun ki aur hajj ki alamtain hain neez un se kaho : yeh koi neki ka kaam nahi hai ke apne gharon mein peechay ki taraf daakhil hotay ho neki to asal mein yeh hai ke aadmi Allah ki narazi se bachay lehaza tum apne gharon mein darwazay hi se aaya karo Albata Allah se drtay raho shayad ke tumhe Falah naseeb ho jaye
  2,190,"aur tum Allah ki raah mein unn logon se lrho, jo tum se lartay hain, magar zayad-ti nah karo ke Allah zayad-ti karne walon ko pasand nahi karta"
  2,191,"un se lrho jahan bhi tumhara unn se muqaabla paish aeye aur inhen nikalu jahan se unhon ne tum ko nikala hai, is liye ke qatal agarchay bura hai, magar fitnah is se bhi ziyada bura hai aur masjid haraam ke qareeb jab taq woh tum se nah lrhin, tum bhi nah lrho, magar jab woh wahan larnay se nah chukein, to tum bhi be takalouf inhen maro ke aisay kafiroon ki yahi saza hai"
  2,192,"phir agar woh baz aa jayen, to jaan lau ke Allah maaf karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  2,193,"tum un se lartay raho yahan taq ke fitnah baqi nah rahay aur deen Allah ke liye ho jaye phir agar woh baz aa jayen, to samajh lau ke zaalmon ke siwa aur kisi par dast Darazi rawa nahi"
  2,194,"mah haraam ka badla haraam hi hai aur tamam hurmatoon ka lehaaz baRabari ke sath hoga lehazajo tumpar dast Darazi kere, tum bhi isi terhan is par dast Darazi karo Albata Allah se drtay raho aur jaan rakho ke Allah inhen logon ke sath hai, jo is ki hudood tornay se parhaiz karte hain"
  2,195,Allah ki raah mein kharch karo aur apne hathon apne aap ko halakat mein nah daalo ahsaan ka tareeqa ikhtiyar karo ke Allah mohsan-ooko pasand karta hai
  2,196,"Allah ki khushnodi ke liye jab hajj aur omre ki niyat karo, to ussay poora karo aur agar kahin ghar jao to jo qurbani muyassar aeye, Allah ki janab mein paish karo aur apne sir nah mun-doojab taq ke qurbani apni jagah nah poanch jaye magar jo shakhs mareez ho ya jis ke sir mein koi takleef ho aur is bana par apna sir mundwa le, to ussay chahiye keh fiyayke tor par rozay rakhay ya sadqa day ya qurbani kere phir agar tumhe aman naseeb ho jaye ( aur tum hajj se pehlay mukkay poanch jao ), to jo shakhs tum mein se hajj ka zamana anay taq omre ka faida uthaye, woh hasb Maqdoor qurbani day, aur a gir qurbani muyassar nah ho, to teen rozay hajj ke zamane mein aur saat ghar poanch kar, iss terhan poooray das rozay rakh le yeh riayat unn logon ke liye hai, jin ke ghar baar masjid haraam ke qareeb nah hon Allah ke inn ehkaam ki khilaaf warzi se bachcho aur khoob jaan lau ke Allah sakht saza dainay wala hai"
  2,197,"hajj ke mahinay sab ko maloom hain jo shakhs un muqarrar mahino mein hajj ki niyat kere, ussay khabardaar rehna chahiye ke hajj ke douran is se koi shehwani feal, koi bad amli, koi larai jhagrre ki baat sarzad nah ho aur jo naik kaam tum karo ge, woh Allah ke ilm mein hoga safar hajj ke liye zaad raah sath le jao, aur sab se behtar zaad raah parhaiz gari hai pas ae hosh mndo! Meer y na farmani se parhaiz karo"
  2,198,"aur agar hajj ke sath sath apne Rab ka fazl bhi talaash karte jao, to is mein koi muzaiqa nahi phir jab Arfat se chalo, to Musher haraam ( mzdlfh ) ke paas theharkar Allah ko yaad karo aur uss terhan yaad karo, jis ki hadaayat is ne tumhe di hai, warna is se pehlay tum log bhatkay hue thay"
  2,199,"phir jahan se sab log palatne hain wahein se tum bhi paltoo aur Allah se maffi chaho, yaqeenan woh maaf karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  2,200,"phir jab apne hajj ke arkaan ada kar chicco, to jis terhan pehlay apne aaba o ajdaad ka zikar karte thay, uss terhan ab Allah ka zikar karo, balkay is se bhi barh kar ( magar Allah ko yaad karne walay logon mein bhi bohat farq hai ) unn mein se koi to aisa hai, jo kehta hai ke ae hamaray Rab, hamein duniya hi mein sab kuch deeday aisay shakhs ke liye akhirat mein koi hissa nahi"
  2,201,aur koi kehta hai ke ae hamaray Rab! hamein duniya mein bhi bhalai day aur akhirat mein bhi bhalai aur aag ke azaab se hamein bacha
  2,202,aisay log apni kamaai ke mutabiq ( dono jagah ) hissa payen ge aur Allah ko hisaab chkate kuch der nahi lagti
  2,203,"yeh ginti ke chand roz hain, jo tumhe Allah ki yaad mein busr karne chahaiyn phir jo koi jaldi kar ke do hi din mein wapas ho gaya to koi harj nahi, aur jo kuch der ziyada tehr kar palta to bhi koi harj nahi basharte-keh yeh din is ne taqwa ke sath busr kiye ho Allah ki nafarmani se bachcho aur khoob jaan rakho ke aik roz is ke huzoor mein tumhari paishi honay wali hai"
  2,204,"insanon mein koi to aisa hai, jis ki baatein duniya ki zindagi mein tumhe bohat bhali maloom hoti hain, aur apni naik niyati par woh baar baar khuda ko gawah tehra taa hai, magar haqeeqat mein woh bad tareen dushman haq hota hai"
  2,205,"jab ussay Iqtidaar haasil ho jata hai, to zameen mein uss ki saari daud dhoop is liye hoti hai ke fasaad phelaaye, khaiton ko ghaarat kere aur nasal insani ko tabah kere halan ke Allah ( jisay woh gawah bana raha tha ) fasaad ko hargiz pasand nahi karta"
  2,206,"aur jab is se kaha jata hai ke Allah se dar, to apne Waqar ka khayaal uss ko gunah par jama deta hai aisay shakhs ke liye to bas jahannum hi kaafi hai aur woh bohat bura thikana hai"
  2,207,"doosri taraf insanon hi mein koi aisa bhi hai, jo Raza ye Ellahi ki talab mein apni jaan کھپا deta hai aur aisay bundon par Allah bohat meharban hai"
  2,208,ae imaan laane walo! tum poooray ke poooray islam mein aa jao aur shetan ki pairwi nah karo ke woh tumhara khula dushman hai
  2,209,"jo saaf saaf Hadayat tumahray pa seen aa chuki hain, agar un ko pa lainay ke baad phir tum ne lazishkhayi, to khoob jaan rakho ke Allah sab par ghalib aur hakeem o Dana hai"
  2,210,"( inn saari nsihton aur hdayton ke baad bhi log seedhay nah hon, to ) kya ab woh iss ke muntazir hain ke Allah baadalon ka chiter lagaye firshton ke paray sa th liye khud samnay aa mojood ho aur faisla hi kar dala jaye? aakhir-kaar saaray mamlaat paish to Allah hi ke huzoor honay walay hain"
  2,211,bani Israel se pucho : kaisi khuli khuli nishanain hum ne unhen dikhayi hain ( aur phir yeh bhi inhen se pooch lau ke ) Allah ki Nemat panay ke baad jo qoum is ko shqawat se badalti hai ussay Allah kaisi sakht saza dayta hai
  2,212,"jin logon ne kufar ki raah ikhtiyar ki hai, unn ke liye duniya ki zindagi barri mehboob o dil pasand bana di gayi hai aisay log imaan ki raah ikhtiyar karne walon ka mazaq uratay hain, magar qayamat ke roz parhaiz gaar log hi unn ke muqablay mein aliiiii maqam hon ge raha duniya ka rizaq, to Allah ko ikhtiyar hai, jisay chahay be hisaab day"
  2,213,"ibtida mein sab log aik hi tareeqa par thay ( phir yeh haalat baqi nah rahi aur ikhtilafat runuma hue ) tab Allah ne nabi beje jo raast rawi par basharat dainay walay aur kaj rawi ke nataij se darane walay thay, aur unn ke sath kitaab Bar haq nazil ki taakay haq ke baray mein logon ke darmain jo ikhtilafat runuma hogaye thay, un ka faisla kere ( aur un ikhtilafat ke runuma honay ki wajah yeh nah thi ke ibtida mein logon ko haq bataya nahi gaya tha nahi, ) ikhtilaaf unn logon ne kya, jinhein haq ka amal diya chuka tha onhon ne roshan Hadayat pa lainay ke baad mehez is ke liye haq ko chore kar mukhtalif tareeqay nikalay ke woh aapas mein zayad-ti karna chahtay thay pas jo log Anabia par imaan le aeye, inhen Allah ne apne azan se uss haq ka rasta dikha diya, jis mein logon ne ikhtilaaf kya tha Allah jisay chahta hai, raah raast dikha deta hai"
  2,214,"phir kya tum logon ne yeh samajh rakha hai ke yuhin jannat ka dakhla tumhe mil jaye ga, halaank abhi tum par woh sab kuch nahi guzra hai, jo tum se pehlay imaan laane walon par guzar chuka hai? unn par skhtyan guzren, museebatein ayen, hila maaray gay, hatta ke waqtka Rasool aur is ke saathi ahal imaan cheekh utthay ke Allah ki madad kab aeye gi uss waqt inhen tasalii di gayi ke haan Allah ki madad qareeb hai"
  2,215,"log puchhte hain ke hum kya kharch karen? jawab do ke jo maal bhi tum kharch karo apne walidain par, rishte daaron par, yatimon aur miskeeno aur musafiron par kharch karo aur jo bhalai bhi tum karo ge, Allah is se bakhabar hoga"
  2,216,"tumhe jung ka hukum diya gaya hai aur woh tumhe nagawaar hai ho sakta hai ke aik cheez tumhe nagawaar ho aur wohi tumahray liye behtar ho aur ho sakta hai ke aik cheez tumhe pasand ho aur wohi tumahray liye buri ho Allah jaanta hai, tum nahi jantay"
  2,217,"log puchhte hain mah haraam mein larna kaisa hai? kaho : iss mein lar na bohat bura hai, magar raah khuda se logon ko rokna aur Allah se kufar karna aur masjid haraam ka rasta khuda paraston par band karna aur haram ke rehne walon ko wahan se nikalna Allah ke nazdeek iss se bhi ziyada bura hai aur fitnah khonrizi se shadeed tar hai woh to tum se larray hi jayen ge hatta ke agar unn ka bas chalay, to tumhe iss deen se phira le jayen ( aur yeh khoob samajh lau ke ) tum mein se jo koi is deen se phiray ga aur kufar ki haalat mein jaan day ga, is ke aamaal duniya aur akhirat dono mein zaya ho jayen ge aisay sab log jahanumi hain aur hamesha jahannum hi mein rahen ge"
  2,218,"bakhalaaf iss ke jo log imaan laaye hain aur jinhon ne khuda ki raah mein apna ghar baar chorra aur jehaad kya hai, woh rehmat Ellahi ke jaaiz umeed waar hain aur Allah un ki lagzishon ko maaf karne wala aur apni rehmat se inhen nawazne wala hai"
  2,219,"puchhte hain : sharaab aur juye ka kya hukum hai? kaho : un dono cheezon mein barri khaRabi hai agarchay un mein logon ke liye kuch munafe bhi hain, magar un ka gunah unn ke faiday se bohat ziyada hai puchhte hain : hum raah khuda mein kya kharch karen? kaho : jo kuch tumhari zaroorat se ziyada ho is terhan Allah tumahray liye saaf saaf ehkaam bayan karta hai, shayad ke tum duniya aur akhirat dono ki fikar karo"
  2,220,"puchhte hain : yatimon ke sath kya maamla kya jaye? kaho : jis tarz amal mein un ke liye bhalai ho, wohi ikhtiyar karna behtar hai agar tum apna aur unn ka kharch aur rehna sehna mushtarik rakho, to is mein koi muzaiqa nahi aakhir woh tumahray bhai band hi to hain buraiee karne walay aur bhalai karne walay, dono ka haal Allah par roshan hai Allah chahta to is muamlay mein tum par sakhti karta, magar woh sahib ikhtiyar honay ke sath sahib hikmat bhi hai"
  2,221,"tum mushriq aurton se hargiz nikah nah karna, jab taq ke woh imaan nah le ayen aik momin londi mushriq shareef zadi se behtar hai, agarchay woh tumhe bohat pasand ho aur apni aurton ke nikah mushriq mardon se kabhi nah karna, jab taq ke woh imaan nah le ayen aik momin ghulam mushriq shareef se behtar hai agarchay woh tumhe bohat pasand ho yeh log tumhe aag ki taraf bulatay hain aur Allah apne azan se tum ko jannat aur mughfirat ki taraf bulaataa hai, aur woh apne ehkaam wazeh tor par logon ke samnay bayan karta hai, tawaqqa hai ke woh sabaq lain ge aur nasihat qubool karen ge"
  2,222,"puchhte hain : haiz ka kya hukum hai? kaho : woh aik gandagi ki haalat hai is mein aurton se allag raho aur un ke qareeb nah jao, jab taq ke woh pak saaf nah ho jayen phir jab woh pak ho jayen, to unn ke paas jao uss terhan jaissa ke Allah ne tum ko hukum diya hai Allah unn logon ko pasand karta hai, jo badi se baz rahen aur pakizgee ikhtiyar karen"
  2,223,"tumhari aurtain tumhari khityan hain tumhe ikhtiyar hai, jis terhan chaho, apni khaiti mein jao, magar apne mustaqbil ki fikar karo aur Allah ki narazi se bachcho khoob jaan lau ke tumhe aik din uss se milna hai aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! jo tumhari Hadayat ko maan lain inhen Falah o Saadat ka musardah suna do"
  2,224,"Allah ke naam ko aisi kasmain khanay ke liye istemaal nah karo, jin se maqsood neki aur taqwa aur bandgaan khuda ki bhalai ke kamon se baz rehna ho Allah tumhari saari baatein sun raha hai aur sab kuch jaanta hai"
  2,225,"jo be maienay kasmain tum bulaa iradah kha liya karte ho, unn par Allah girift nahi karta, magar jo kasmain tum sachey dil se khatay ho, unn ki baz purse woh zaroor kere ga Allah bohat Dur guzar karne wala aur Burdbar hai"
  2,226,"jo log apni aurton se talluq nah rakhnay ki qasam kha baithy hain, unn ke liye chaar mahinay ki mohlat hai agar unhon ne rujoo kar liya, to Allah maaf karne wala aur Raheem hai"
  2,227,aur agar onhon ne Talaq hi ki thaan li ho to jaane rahen ke Allah sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai
  2,228,"jin aurton ko Talaq di gayi ho, woh teen martaba ayyaam mahvari anay taq apne aap ko rokay rakhen aur unn ke liye yeh jaaiz nahi hai ke Allah ne unn ke reham mein jo kuch Khalq farmaya ho, ussay chupayen unhen hargiz aisa nah karna chahiye, agar woh Allah aur roz aakhir par imaan rakhti hain unn ke shohar taluqaat durust kar lainay par amaada hon, to woh iss adt ke douran unhen phir apni zojiat mein wapas le lainay ke haq daar hain aurton ke liye bhi Maroof tareeqay par waisay hi haqooq hain, jaisay mardon ke haqooq unn par hain Albata mardon ko unn par aik darja haasil hai aur sab par Allah ghalib Iqtidaar rakhnay wala aur hakeem o Dana mojood hai"
  2,229,"Talaq do baar hai phir ya to seedhi terhan aurat ko rok liya jaye ya bhallay tareeqay se is ko rukhsat kar diya jaye aur rukhsat kar te hue aisa karna tumahray liye jaaiz nahi hai ke jo kuch tum inhen day chuke ho, uss mein se kuch wapas le lau Albata yeh soorat mustasna hai ke zojin ko Allah ke hudood par qaim nah reh saknay ka andesha ho aisi soorat mein agar tumhe yeh khauf ho ke woh dono hudood Ellahi par qaim nah rahen ge, to unn dono ke darmain yeh maamla ho jaane mein muzaiqa nahi ke aurat apne shohar ko kuch muawza day kar alehadgi haasil kar le yeh Allah ke muqarrar kardah hudood hain, inn se tajawaz nah karo aur jo log hudood Ellahi se tajawaz karen, wohi zalim hain"
  2,230,"phir agar ( do baara Talaq dainay ke baad shohar ne aurat ko teesri baar ) Talaq day di to woh aurat phir is ke liye halal nah hogi, ila yeh ke is ka nikah kisi dosray shakhs se ho aur woh usay Talaq deeday tab agar pehla shohar aur yeh aurat dono yeh khayaal karen ke hudood Ellahi par qaim rahen ge, to un ke liye aik dosray ki taraf Raju a kar lainay mein koi muzaiqa nahi yeh Allah ki muqarrar kardah hade hain, jinhein woh unn logon ki hadaayat ke liye wazeh kar raha hai, jo ( is ki hudood ko tornay ka injaam ) jantay hain"
  2,231,"aur jab tum aurton ko Talaq day do aur un ki adt poori honay ko aa jaye, to ya bhallay tareeqay se inhen rok lau ya bhallay tareeqay se rukhsat kar do mehez satanay ki khatir inhen nah rokay rakhna yeh zayad-ti hogi aur jo aisa kere ga, woh Dur haqeeqat aap apne hi oopar zulm kere ga Allah ki ayaat ka khail nah banaao bhool nah jao ke Allah ne kis Nemat Uzma se tumhe Sarfraz kya hai woh tumhe nasihat karta hai ke jo kitaab aur hikmat uss ne tum par nazil ki hai, is ka ehtram malhooz rakho Allah se daro aur khoob jaan lau ke Allah ko har baat ki khabar hai"
  2,232,"jab tum apni aurton ko Talaq day chicco aur woh apni adt poori kar lain, to phir is mein Maney nah ho ke woh apne zair tajweez shohron se nikah kar lain, jab ke woh Maroof tareeqay se baahum مناکحت par raazi hon tumhe nasihat ki jati hai ke aisi harkat hargiz nah karna, agar tum Allah aur roz aakhir par imaan laane walay ho tumahray liye shaista aur pakeeza tareeqa yahi hai ke is se baz raho Allah jaanta hai, tum nahi jantay"
  2,233,"jo baap chahtay hon ke un ki oola daal poori muddat rzaat taq doodh piyay, to maaen apne bachon ko kaamil do saal doodh pilain iss soorat mein bachay ke baap ko Maroof tareeqay se inhen khana kapra dena hoga magar kisi par is ki wusat se barh kar baar nah daalna chahiye nah to maa ko iss wajah se takleef mein dala jaye ke bacha is ka hai, aur nah baap hi ko is wajah se tang kya jaye ke bacha is ka hai doodh pilanay wali ka yeh haq jaissa bachay ke baap par hai waisa hi is ke waris par bhi hai lekin agar fariqain bahami razamandi aur mashwaray se doodh chhurana chahain, to aisa karne mein koi muzaiqa nahi aur agar tumhara khayaal apni aulaad ko kisi ghair aurat se doodh plwane ka ho, to is mein bhi koi harj nahi bashar tik_h is ka jo kuch muawza tey karo, woh Maroof tareeqay par ada kar do Allah se daro aur jaan rakho ke jo kuch tum karte ho, sab Allah ki nazar mein hai"
  2,234,"tum mein se jo log mar jayen, unn ke peechay agar unn ki biwiyan zindah hon, to woh apne aap ko chaar mahinay, das din rokay rakhen phir jab un ki adt poori ho jaye, to inhen ikhtiyar hai, apni zaat ke muamlay mein Maroof tareeqay se jo chahain, karen tum par is ki koi zimma daari nahi Allah tum sab ke aamaal se bakhabar hai"
  2,235,"zamana adt mein khuwa tum unn bewa aurton ke sath mangni ka iradah isharay kanai-ay mein zahir kar do, khuwa dil mein chupaye rakho, dono sooraton mein koi muzaiqa nahi Allah jaanta hai ke unn ka khayaal to tumahray dil mein aeye ga hi magar dekho! khufia ehad o Paiman nah karna agar koi baat karni hai, to Muarif tareeqay se karo aur Aqab nikah bandhnay ka faisla uss waqt taq nah karo, jab taq ke adt poori nah ho jaye khoob samajh lau ke Allah tumahray dilon ka haal taq jaanta hai lehaza is se daro aur yeh bhi jaan lau ke Allah Burdbar hai, choti choti baton se dar guzar farmata hai"
  2,236,"tum par kuch gina hay nahi, agar apni tum aurton ko Talaq day do qabal is ke ke haath laganay ki nobat aeye ya mohar muqarrar ho is soorat mein unhen kuch nah kuch dena zaroor chahiye khush haal aadmi apni mqdrt ke mutabiq aur ghareeb apni mqdrt ke mutabiq Maroof tareeqa se day yeh haq hai naik admion par"
  2,237,"aur agar tum ne haath laganay se pehlay Talaq di hai, lekin mohar muqarrar kya ja chuka ho, to is soorat mein nisf mohar dena hoga yeh aur baat hai ke aurat narmi bartay ( aur mohar nah le ) ya woh mard, jis ke ikhtiyar mein Aqab nikah hai, narmi se kaam le ( aur poora mohar deeday ), aur tum ( yani mard ) narmi se kaam lau, to yeh taqwa se ziyada munasbat rakhta hai aapas ke mamlaat mein Fayazi ko nah bhulo tumahray aamaal ko Allah dekh raha hai"
  2,238,"apni namazon ki nighdasht rakho, khasosan aisi namaz ki jo mhasn salaat ki ja ma ho Allah ke agay is terhan kharray ho, jaisay fir maa bardaar ghulam khar y hotay hain"
  2,239,"bad amni ki haalat ho, to khuwa paidal ho, khuwa sawaar, jis terhan mumkin ho, namaz parho aur jab aman muyassar aajay, to Allah ko uss tareeqay se yaad karo, jo uss ne tumhe sikha diya hai, jis se tum pehlay na waaqif thay"
  2,240,"tum mein se jo logon wafaat payen aur peechay biwiyan chore rahay hon, unn ko chahiye ke apni biwion ke haq mein yeh wasiyat kar jayen ke aik saal taq un ko nan o nfqh diya jaye aur woh ghar se nah nikaali jayen phir agar woh khud nikal jayen, to apni zaat ke muamlay mein Maroof tareeqay se woh jo kuch bhi karen, is ki koi zimma daari tum par nahi hai Allah sab par ghalib Iqtidaar rakhnay wala aur hakeem o Dana hai"
  2,241,"isi terhan jin aurton ko Talaq di gayi ho, inhen bhi munasib tor par kuch nah kuch day kar rukhsat kya jaye yeh haq hai mut-taqi logon par"
  2,242,iss terhan Allah apne ehkaam tumhe saaf saaf batata hai umeed hai ke tum samajh boojh kar kaam karo ge
  2,243,"tum ne unn logon ke haal par bhi kuch ghhor kya, jo mout ke dar se apne ghar baar chore kar niklay thay aur hazaron ki tadaad mein thay? Allah ne unn se farmaya : mar jao phir uss ne unn ko dobarah zindagi bakhsh haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah ensaan par bara fazl frmane wala hai magar aksar log shukar ada nahi karte"
  2,244,muslmano! Allah ki raah mein jung karo aur khoob jaan rakho ke Allah suneney wala aur jan-nay wala hai
  2,245,"tum mein kon hai jo Allah ko qarz husn day taakay Allah ussay kayi gina barha charha kar wapas kere? ghatana bhi Allah ke ikhtiyar mein hai aur barhana bhi, aur usi ki taraf tumhe palat kar jana hai"
  2,246,"phir tum ne uss muamlay par bhi ghhor kya, jo( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)ke baad sardaraan bani Israel ko paish aaya tha? onhon ne apne nabi se kaha : hamaray liye aik badshah muqarrar kar do taakay hum Allah ki raah mein jung karen nabi ne poocha : kahin aisa to nah hoga ke tum ko larai ka hukum diya jaye aur phir tum nah lrho woh kehnay lagey : bhala yeh kaisay ho sakta hai ke hum raah khuda mein nah lrhin, jabkay hamein apne gharon se nikaal diya gaya hai aur hamaray baal bachay hum se judda kar diye gay hain magar jab un ko jung ka hukum diya gaya, to aik qaleel tadaad ke siwa woh sab peeth mourr gay, aur Allah un mein se aik aik zalim ko jaanta hai"
  2,247,"unn ke nabi ne un se kaha ke Allah ne Taloot ko tumahray liye badshah muqarrar kya hai yeh sun kar woh bolay :"" hum par badshah ban'nay ka woh kaisay haqdaar ho gaya? uss ke muqablay mein badshahi ke hum ziyada mustahiq hain woh to koi bara ma l- daar aadmi nahi hai"" nabi ne jawab diya :"" Allah ne tumahray muqablay mein isi ko muntakhib kya hai aur is ko dimaghi o jismani dono qisam ki ahliyaten farawani ke sath ataa farmai hain aur Allah ko ikhtiyar hai ke apna malik jisay chahay day, Allah barri wusat rakhta hai aur sab kuch uss ke ilm mein hai """
  2,248,"is ke sath unn ke nabi ne unn ko yeh bhi bataya ke"" khuda ki taraf se uss ke badshah muqarrar honay ki alamat yeh hai ke is ke ehad mein woh sandooq tumhe wapas mil jaye ga, jis mein tumahray Rab ki taraf se tumahray liye sukoon qalb ka samaan hai, jis mein all( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)aur all Haroon ke chhorey hue tabarruqaat hain, aur jis ko is waqt farishtay sambhale hue hain agar tum momin ho, to yeh tumahray liye bohat barri nishani hai"
  2,249,"phir jab Taloot lashkar le kar chala, to uss ne kaha :"" aik darya par Allah ki taraf se tumhari azmaish honay wali hai jwas ka pani piyay ga, woh mera saathi nahi mera saathi sirf woh hai jo is se pyaas nah bujhaye, haan aik aadh chalo koi pi le, to pi le"" magar aik giroh qaleel ke siwa woh sab is darya se sairaab hue phir jab Taloot aur is ke saathi musalman darya paar kar ke agay barhay, to onhon ne Taloot se keh diya ke aaj hum mein Jalut aur is ke lashkaron ka muqaabla karne ki taaqat nahi hai lekin jo log yeh samajte thay ke inhen aik din Allah se milna hai, unhon ne kaha :"" baarha aisa howa hai ke aik qaleel giroh Allah ke azan se aik barray giroh par ghalib agaya hai Allah sabr karne walon ka saathi hai """
  2,250,"aur jab woh Jalut aur is ke lashkaron ke muqaabla par niklay, to unhon ne dua ki :"" ae hamaray Rab hum par sabr ka Faizan kar, hamaray qadam jama day aur is kafir giroh par hamein fatah naseeb kar """
  2,251,"aakhir ka ray Allah ke azan se onhon ne kafiroon ko maar bhgaya aur DAWOD ne Jalut ko qatal kar diya aur Allah ne usay saltanat aur hikmat se nawaza aur jin jin cheezon ka chaha, is ko ilm diya agar is terhan Allah insanon ke aik giroh ko dosray giroh ke zariye htata nah rehta, to zameen ka nizaam baggar jata, lekin duniya ke logon par Allah ka bara fazl hai ( ke woh iss terhan dafaa fasaad ka intizam karta rehta hai )"
  2,252,"yeh Allah ki ayaat hain, jo hum theek theek tum ko suna rahay hain aur tum yaqeenan un logon mein se ho, jo rasool bana kar beje gay hain"
  2,253,"yeh rasool ( jo hamari taraf se insanon ki hadaayat par mamoor hue ) hum ne un ko aik dosray se barh charh kar martabay ataa kiye un mein koi aisa tha jis se khuda khud hum kalaam howa, kisi ko is ne doosri hisiton se buland darjay diye, aur aakhir mein ( hazrat ) Eesa Ibn maryam(alh-e-salam) ko roshan nishanain ataa kee aur rooh pak se is ki madad ki agar Allah chahta, to mumkin nah tha ke inn rasloon Rasolo-n ke baad jo log roshan nishanain dekh chuke thay, woh aapas mein lartay magar ( Allah ki Mushiyat yeh nah thi ke woh logon ko jabran ikhtilaaf se rokay, is wajah se ) unhon ne baahum ikhtilaaf kya, phir koi imaan laya aur kisi ne kufar ki raah ikhtiyar ki haan, Allah chahta, to woh hargiz nah lartay, magar Allah jo chahta hai karta hai"
  2,254,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jo kuch maal mata hum ne tum ko bakhsha hai, is mein se kharch karo, qabal is ke ke woh din aeye, jis mein nah kharedo farokht hogi, nah dosti kaam aeye gi aur nah sifarish chalay gi aur zalim asal mein wohi hain, jo kufar ki rawish ikhtiyar karte hain"
  2,255,"Allah , woh zindah Javed hasti, jo tamam kaayenaat ko sambhale hue hai, uss ke siwa koi khuda nahi hai woh nah sota hai aur nah ussay ongh lagti hai zameen aur asmano mein jo kuch hai, usi ka hai kon hai jo uss ki janab mein uss ki ijazat ke baghair sifarish kar sakay? jo kuch bundon ke samnay hai usay bhi woh jaanta hai aur jo kuch unn se oojhal hai, is se bhi woh waaqif hai aur uss ki maloomat mein se koi cheez unn ki girift idraak mein nahi askati ila yeh ke kisi cheez ka ilm woh khud hi unn ko dena chahay uss ki hukoomat asmano aur zameen par chhai hui hai aur unn ki nigehbani is ke liye koi thaka dainay wala kaam nahi hai bas wohi aik buzurag o bartar zaat hai"
  2,256,"deen ke muamlay mein koi zor zabardasti nahi hai sahih baat ghalat khayalat se a lag chhant kar rakh di gayi hai ab jo koi Taghoot ka inkaar kar ke Allah par imaan le aaya, uss ne aik aisa mazboot sahara thaam liya, jo kabhi totnay wala nahi, aur Allah ( jis ka sahara is ne liya hai ) sab kuch suneney aur jan-nay wala hai"
  2,257,"jo log imaan laatay hain, unn ka haami o madadgaar Allah hai aur woh un ko tarikeon se roshni mein nikaal lata hai aur jo log kufar ki raah ikhtiyar karte hain, unn ke haami o madad gaar Taghoot hain aur woh inhen roshni se tarikeon ki taraf khech le jatay hain yeh aag mein jaane walay log hain, jahan yeh hamesha rahen ge"
  2,258,"kya tum ne uss shakhs ke haal par ghhor nahi kya, jis ne ibrahim se jhagra kya tha? jhagra iss baat par ke ibrahim ka Rab kon hai, aur is bana par ke is shakhs ko Allah ne hukoomat day rakhi thi jab ibrahim ne kaha ke"" mera Rab woh hai, jis ke ikhtiyar mein zindagi aur mout hai, to uss ne jawab diya :"" zindagi aur mout mere ikhtiyar mein hai"" ibrahim ne kaha :"" acha, Allah Sooraj ko mashriq se nkalta hai, to zara ussay maghrib se nikaal laa"" yeh sun kar woh munkir haq shashdar reh gaya, magar Allah zaalmon ko raah raast nahi dekhaya karta"
  2,259,"ya phir misaal ke tor par uss shakhs ko dekho, jis ka guzar aik aisi bastii par howa, jo apni chaton par ondhee giri pari thi uss ne kaha :"" yeh abadi, jo halaak ho chuki hai, usay Allah kis terhan dobarah zindagi bakhshay ga ?"" is par Allah ne is ki rooh qabz kar li aur woh so baras taq murda para raha phir Allah ne usay dobarah zindagi bakhsh aur is se poocha :"" batao, kitni muddat parre rahay ho ?"" uss ne kaha :"" aik din ya chand ghantay raha hon ga"" farmaya :"" tum par so baras isi haalat mein guzar chuke hain ab zara apne khanay aur pani ko dekho ke is mein zara tagayur nahi aaya hai doosri taraf zara apne gadhay ko bhi dekho ( ke iss ka panjar taq بوسید hay ho raha hai ) aur yeh hum ne is liye kya hai ke hum tumhe logon ke liye aik nishani bana dena chahtay hain phir dekho ke hadion ke iss panjar ko hum kis terhan utha kar gosht post is par charhatay hain"" is terhan jab haqeeqat is ke samnay bilkul numaya ho gayi, to is ne kaha :"" mein jaanta hon ke Allah har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai """
  2,260,"aur woh waqea bhi paish e nazar rahay, jab ibrahim ne kaha tha ke :"" mere maalik, mujhe dikha day, to mُrdon ko kaisay zindah karta hai"" farmaya :"" kya to imaan nahi rakhta ?"" uss ne arz kya"" imaan to rakhta hon, magar dil ka itminan darkaar hai"" farmaya :"" acha to chaar parinday le aur un ko apne se manoos kar le phir un ka aik aik juz aik aik pahar par rakh day phir un ko pukaar, woh tairay paas doray chalay ayen ge khoob jaan le ke Allah nihayat ba Iqtidaar aur hakeem hai """
  2,261,"jo log apne maal Allah ki raah mein sirf karte hain, unn ke kharch ki misaal aisi hai, jaisay aik dana boya jaye aur is se saat balain nikleen aur har baal mein so danay hon isi terhan Allah jis ke amal ko chahta hai, afzoni ataa farmata hai woh farakh dast bhi hai aur Aleem bhi"
  2,262,"jo log apne maal Allah ki raah mein kharch karte hain aur kharch kar ke phir ahsaan jatate, nah dukh dete hain, unn ka ajar unn ke Rab ke paas hai aur un ke liye kisi ranj aur khauf ka mauqa nahi"
  2,263,"aik meetha bol aur kisi nagawaar baat par zara si chasham poshi uss khairaat se behtar hai, jis ke peechay dukh ho Allah be niaz hai aur burdbaari uss ki sift hai"
  2,264,"ae imaan laane walo! apne sadqat ko ahsaan jta kar aur dukh day kar uss shakhs ki terhan khaak mein nah mila do, jo apna maal mehez logon ke dikhaane ko kharch karta hai aur nah Allah par aima noon rakhta hai, nah akhirat par uss ke kharch ki misaal aisi hai, jaisay aik chattaan thi, jis par matti ki teh jami hui thi is par jab zor ka meen barsa, to saari matti beh gayi aur saaf chattaan ki chattaan reh gayi aisay log apne nazdeek khairaat kar ke jo neki kamate hain, is se kuch bhi unn ke haath nahi aata, aur kafiroon ko seedhi raah dikhnana Allah ka dastoor nahi hai"
  2,265,"bakhalaaf iss ke jo lau g apne maal mehez Allah ki Raza joi ke liye dil ke poooray Sabaat o qarar ke sath kharch karte hain, un ke kharch ki misaal aisi hai, jaisay kisi satah murtafa par aik baagh ho agar zor ki baar sh ho jaye to do gina phal laaye, aur agar zor ki barish nah bhi ho to aik halki phwaar hi uss ke liye kaafi ho jaye tum jo kuch karte ho, sab Allah ki nazar mein hai"
  2,266,"kya tum mein se koi yeh pasand karta hai ke is ke paas aik hara bhara baagh ho, nﮦron se sairaab, khajoron aur angarro aur hrqsm ke phalon se lada howa, aur woh ain uss waqt aik taiz bagoole ki zad mein aa kar jhulas jaye, jabkay woh khud boorha ho aur is ke kam sun bachay abhi kisi Laiq nah hon? is terhan Allah apni baatein tumahray samnay bayan karta hai, shayad ke tum ghhor o fikar karo"
  2,267,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jo maal tum ne kamaye hain aur jo kuch hum ne zameen se tumahray liye nikala hai, uss se behtar hissa raah khuda mein kharch karo aisa nah ho ke is ki raah mein dainay ke liye buri se buri cheez chhantnay ki koshish karne lagu, halaank wohi cheez agar koi tumhe day, to tum hargiz ussay laina gawara nah karo ge ila yeh ke is ko qubool karne mein tum aghmaz bart jao tumhe jaan laina chahiye ke Allah be niaz hai aur behtareen sifaat se mutsif hai"
  2,268,"shetan tumhe muflisi se darata hai aur sharamnaak tarz amal ikhtiyar karne ki targheeb deta hai, magar Allah tumhe apni bakhshish aur fazl ki umeed dilaata hai Allah bara farakh dast aur Dana hai"
  2,269,"jis ko chahta hai hikmat ataa karta hai, aur jis ko hikmat mili, ussay haqeeqat mein barri doulat mil gayi inn baton se sirf wohi log sabaq letay hain, jo danishmand hain"
  2,270,"tum ne jo kuch bhi kharch kya ho aur jo Nazar bhi maani ho, Allah ko uss ka ilm hai, aur zaalmon ka koi madadgaar nahi"
  2,271,"agar apne sadqat alania do, to yeh bhi acha hai, lekin agar chhupa kar haajat mandoon ko do, to yeh tumahray haq mein ziyada behtar hai tumhari bohat si buraiyan iss tarz amal se mehv ho jati hain aur jo kuch tum karte hue Allah ko bahar haal uss ki khabar hai"
  2,272,"logon ko hadaayat bakhash dainay ki zimmay daari tum par nahi hai hadaayat to Allah hi jisay chahta hai bkhshta hai aur khairaat mein jo maal tum kharch karte ho woh tumahray apne liye bhala hai aakhir tum isi liye to kharch karte ho ke Allah ki Raza haasil ho to jo kuch maal tum khairaat mein kharch karo ge, is ka poora poora ajar tumhe diya jaye ga aur tumhari haq talfi hargiz nah hogi"
  2,273,khaas tor par madad ke mustahiq woh tang dast log hain jo Allah ke kaam mein aisay ghar gay hain ke apni zaati ksb muaash ke liye zameen mein koi daud dhoop nahi kar saktay un ki khud daari dekh kar nawaqif aadmi gumaan karta hai ke yeh khush haal hain tum un ke cheharon se un ki androoni haalat pehchan satke ho magar woh aisay log nahi hain ke logon ke peechay par kar kuch mangeen unn ki eaanat mein jo kuch maal tum kharch karo ge woh Allah se posheeda nah rahay ga
  2,274,jo lau g apne maal shab o roz khulay aur chupay kharch karte hain un ka ajar un ke Rab ke paas hai aur unn ke liye kisi khauf aur ranj ka maqam nahi
  2,275,"magar jo log sood khatay hain, aُ noon ka haal uss shakhs ka sa hota hai, jisay shetan ne chhoo kar bawla kar diya ho aur is haalat mein unn ke mubtala honay ki wajah yeh hai ke woh kehte hain :"" tijarat bhi to aakhir sood hi jaisi cheez hai "", halaank Allah ne tijarat ko halal kya hai aur sood ko haraam lehaza jis shakhs ko is ke Rab ki taraf se yeh nasihat puhanche aur aindah ke liye woh sood khori se baz aa jaye, to jo kuch woh pehlay kha chuka, so kha chuka, is ka maamla Allah ke hawalay hai aur jo iss hukum ke baad phir isi harkat ka iada kere, woh jahanumi hai, jahan woh hamesha rahay ga"
  2,276,Allah sood ka muth maar deta hai aur sadqat ko nasho o numa deta hai aur Allah kisi nashukray bad amal ensaan ko pasand nahi karta
  2,277,"haan, jo log imaan le ayen aur naik amal karen aur namaz qaim karen aurzakat den, unn ka ajar be shak un ke Rab ke paas hai aur un ke liye kisi khauf aur ranj ka mauqa nahi"
  2,278,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, khuda se daro aur jo kuch tumhara sood logon par baqi reh gaya hai, usay chore do, agar waqai tum imaan laaye ho"
  2,279,"lekin agar tum ne aisa nah kya, to aagah ho jao ke Allah aur uskay rasool ki taraf se tumahray khilaaf elaan jung hai ab bhi tauba kar lau ( aur sood chore do ) to apna asal sarmaya lainay ke tum haq daar ho nah tum zulm karo, nah tum par zulm kya jaye"
  2,280,"tumhara qarz daar tang dast ho, to haath khilnay taq ussay mohlat do, aur jo sadqa kar do, to yeh tumahray liye ziyada behtar hai, agar tum samjhoo"
  2,281,"is din ki ruswai o museebat se bachcho, jabkay tum Allah ki taraf wapas ho ge, wahan har shakhs ko is ki kamaai hui neki ya badi ka poora poora badla mil jaye ga aur kisi par zulm hargiz nah hoga"
  2,282,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jab kisi muqarrar muddat ke liye tum aapas mein qarz ka lain deen karo, to usay likh liya karo fariqain ke darmain insaaf ke sathshakhs dastaweez tehreer kere jisay Allah ne likhnay parhnay ki qabliyat bakhsh ho, usay likhnay se inkaar nah karna chahiye woh likhay aur imla woh shakhs karaye jis par haq aata hai ( yani qarz lainay wala ), aur ussay Allah , apne Rab se darna chahiye ke jo maamla tey howa ho is mein koi kami Beshi nah kere lekin agar qarz lainay wala khud nadaan ya zaeef ho, imla nah kara sakta ho, twas ka walii insaaf ke sath imla karaye phir apne mardon se do admion ki is par gawahi kara lau aur agar do mard nah hon to aik mard aur do aurtain hon taakay aik bhool jaye, to doosri usay yaad dila day yeh gawah aisay logon mein se honay chahaiyn, jin ki gawahi tumahray darmain maqbool ho gawahoon ko jab gawah ban'nay ke liye kaha jaye, to inhen inkaar nah karna chahiye maamla khuwa chhota ho ya bara, meyaad ki taayun ke sath is ki dastaweez lkhwa lainay mein tsahl nah karo Allah ke nazdeek yeh tareeqa tumahray liye ziyada mabni Bar insaaf hai, is se shahadat qaim honay mein ziyada sahoolat hoti hai, aur tumahray shukook o shubhat mein mubtala honay ka imkaan kam reh jata hai haan jo tijarti lain deen dast bdst tum log aapas mein karte ho, is ko nah likha jaye to koi harj nahi, magar tijarti muamlay tey karte waqt gawah kar liya karo katib aur gawah ko sataya nah jaye aisa karo ge, to gunah ka irtikaab karo ge Allah ke ghazab se bachcho woh tum ko sahih tareeq amal ki taleem deta hai aur usay har cheez ka ilm hai"
  2,283,"agar tum safar ki haalat mein ho aur dastaweez likhnay ke liye koi katib nah miley, to rehan biqabgh par maamla karo agar tum mein se koi shakhs dosray par bharosa kar ke is ke sath koi maamla kere, to jis par bharosa kya gaya hai, usay chahiye ke amanat ada kere aur Allah , apne Rab se daray aur shahadat hargiz nah chupao jo shahadat chupata hai, is ka dil gunah mein aaloda hai aur Allah tumahray aamaal se bay khabar nahi hai"
  2,284,"asmano aur zameen mein jo kuch hai, sab Allah ka hai tum apne dil ki baatein khuwa zahir karo ya chupao Allah behar haal un ka hisaab tum se le le ga phir usay ikhtiyar hai, jisay chahay, maaf kar day aur jisay chahay, saza day woh har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
  2,285,"rasool uss hadaayat par imaan laya hai jo is ke Rab ki taraf se is par nazil hui hai aur jo log iss rasool ke maan-ne walay hain, unhon ne bhi is hadaayat ko dil se tasleem kar liya hai yeh sab Allah aur is ke firshton aur iss ki kitabon aur is ke Rasolo-n Rasoloo-N ko mantay hain aur un ka qoul yeh hai ke :"" hum Allah keRasoloo-N Rasolo-n ko aik dosray se allag nahi karte, hum ne hukum suna aur itaat qubool ki maalik! hum tujh se khata bakhsh ke taalib hain aur hamein teri hi taraf palatna hai """
  2,286,"Allah kisi mutnaqas par uss ki mqdrt se barh kar zimma daari ka boojh nahi dalta har shakhs ne jo neki kamaai hai, is ka phal isi ke liye hai aur jo badi smiti hai, is ka wabaal isi par hai ( imaan laane walo! tum yun dua kya karo ) ae hamaray Rab! hum se bhool chowk mein jo qasoor ho jayen, un par girift nah kar maalik! hum par woh boojh nah daal, jo to ne hum se pehlay logon par daaley thay parvar-digaar! jis baar ko uthany ki taaqat hum mein nahi hai, woh hum par nah rakh, hamaray sath narmi kar, hum se Dur guzar farma, hum par reham kar, to hamara Mooli hai, kafiroon ke muqablay mein hamari madad kar"
